{"type":"message","id":"2fcf6963","parentId":"4ee481e0","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:53:24.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only 1 session is showing! That's very strange. The status command showed 63 sessions, but sessions_list only returns 1. This could be the issue - the gateway shows many sessions but they're not all accessible via the API.\n\nWait, actually the status output said \"63 active\" sessions, but sessions_list only returns 1. That's very odd. It might be a pagination issue or the sessions_list tool has some filtering.\n\nActually, looking at the deliveryContext: the current session is using `feishu-assistant` account, which is \"周到\". But according to IDENTITY.md, \"来福来财\" should be the quant assistant. Maybe 张玲 is talking to the wrong bot?\n \nSo the 63 sessions are likely from older conversations that aren't being returned by this particular API call. The real question is which Feishu bot \"来福来财\" is supposed to be - it doesn't appear to be configured as a separate account. I should ask the user for more details about how they're trying to interact with it and what exactly happens when it doesn't respond.","thinkingSignature":"8fbdf03054a0c3a0aae57d01612fcfe1998994b284bc46e2a4e93179989728ec"},{"type":"text","text":"没有看到独立的\"来福来财\"会话。当前 OpenClaw 只配置了 2 个飞书账号：\n\n1. **feishu-assistant（周到）** — 这个正在回复你\n2. **main** — 主脑\n\n没有单独的\"来福来财\"机器人账号。\n\n有几个可能：\n\n**可能 A**：你在飞书里发消息给了\"周到\"（当前这个），但期待的是量化系统回答，结果发现没反应。\n\n**可能 B**：\"来福来财\"是另一个飞书机器人，但你没有把它加为 OpenClaw 的 channel 账号，所以消息根本没进来。\n\n你能告诉我：\n1. 你在哪找到\"来福来财\"的？飞书里哪个机器人？\n2. 它是完全没有回复，还是回复过一次然后停了？\n\n这样我才能判断是配置问题、会话卡死、还是账号本身就没接入 OpenClaw。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11138,"output":404,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773921190443}}
