{"type":"message","id":"9f641c2d","parentId":"44b72f75","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:23:45.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what mcporter can do. Let me give them a practical overview based on the SKILL.md I already read.","thinkingSignature":"78a5fbf8211ea952c693fa66fe01dd279d380245ff3cd2058de813ee831a1e04"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n`mcporter` 是 MCP（Model Context Protocol）客户端工具，可以直接调用各种 MCP 服务器上的工具。以下是实际用法：\n\n---\n\n## 查你能用哪些工具\n\n```bash\nmcporter list\n```\n\n会列出所有已配置的 MCP 服务器及其工具。\n\n---\n\n## 调用工具\n\n```\nmcporter call <server>.<tool> 参数\n```\n\n例如：\n- `mcporter call linear.list_issues team=ENG limit:5`\n- `mcporter call \"linear.create_issue(title: \\\"Bug fix\\\")\"`\n\n---\n\n## 配置 MCP 服务器\n\n```bash\n# 添加服务器\nmcporter config add <name> <url>\n\n# OAuth 授权\nmcporter auth <server | url> [--reset]\n\n# 查看当前配置\nmcporter config list\n```\n\n---\n\n## 常见场景\n\n| 场景 | 用法 |\n|---|---|\n| 查 GitHub Issue | `mcporter call github.list_issues owner=seablue1985 repo=openclaw-config state:open` |\n| 发 Slack 消息 | `mcporter call slack.post_message channel=xxx text=\"报告已生成\"` |\n| 读网页内容 | `mcporter call mcp.fetch url=https://example.com` |\n| 跑本地脚本服务 | `mcporter call --stdio \"bun run ./server.ts\" scrape url=https://...` |\n\n---\n\n你想用它连接哪个具体服务？我帮你配。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80,"output":321,"cacheRead":48911,"cacheWrite":4221,"totalTokens":53533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773926609045}}
