{"type":"message","id":"d68daf6c","parentId":"a0c1e401","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:25:33.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the a-share-fusion-report skill since it's the quant-related one, and also check the system architecture doc to understand the integration better.","thinkingSignature":"3c40af14e489a7d6a67363bbc2a42342fa01b37b7235c6ca5020f241d8868462"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v5y2t6ci8hyu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/docs/SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33467,"output":89,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773926729440}}
{"type":"message","id":"961c4dc1","parentId":"d68daf6c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:25:33.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v5y2t6ci8hyu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 个人量化投资系统架构说明（v1）\n\n## 1. 目标\n构建一个可持续运行的个人量化投资系统，覆盖：\n- 数据更新\n- 策略研发\n- 统一回测评估\n- 风控与仓位管理\n- 盘前/盘后自动化\n- 报告与复盘\n- 面向实盘决策的输出\n\n## 2. 系统定位\n当前建议将 `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system` 作为唯一主系统（生产主线）。\n其他目录作为上游数据层或策略实验层，不直接承担生产执行职责。\n\n## 3. 四层一中心架构\n\n### A. 数据层\n职责：标准化提供行情、基本面、指数、持仓、成交等数据。\n\n建议上游来源：\n- `quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis`\n- 同花顺导出/同步脚本\n- Tushare / AkShare\n- 后续可接入 QuestDB\n\n建议统一核心数据对象：\n- `daily_price`\n- `daily_basic`\n- `index_daily`\n- `financial_indicator`\n- `holdings_snapshot`\n- `trades_snapshot`\n- `benchmark_series`\n\n字段标准：\n- 股票代码统一 `ts_code`\n- 日期统一 `trade_date`\n- 行情统一 `open/high/low/close/vol/amount`\n- 基本面统一 `turnover_rate/market_cap/circ_mv/...`\n\n### B. 策略研发层\n职责：策略原型开发、参数试验、回测验证。\n\n建议纳入：\n- `quant_projects/jq_strategies`\n- `quant_projects/qlib`\n- `RD-Agent`\n- 各类 `backtest_*` 脚本\n\n原则：\n- 研发层不直接对接生产执行\n- 所有策略统一输出 `signal` 结构\n\n推荐 signal 结构：\n```csv\ntrade_date,ts_code,signal_type,target_weight,score,strategy_id,comment\n2026-03-09,000001.SZ,BUY,0.10,0.82,smallcap_chip_v4_2,alpha_recover\n```\n\n### C. 风控与组合层\n职责：统一管理仓位、风险、预算与多策略合成。\n\n应独立成模块，不再散落在各策略内部。建议包含：\n- `breadth_guard`\n- `liquidity_guard`\n- `position_sizer`\n- `risk_engine`\n- `blacklist`\n- `portfolio_allocator`\n\n核心原则：\n> 策略负责提出“买什么”，风控负责决定“能不能买、买多少”。\n\n### D. 执行与报告层\n职责：将 signal 转化为订单建议，将系统状态转化为报告和面板。\n\n建议保留在主系统内：\n- 盘前 precheck\n- 订单建议单\n- 净额合并\n- dashboard 生成\n- 每日审计\n- 飞书推送\n- 后续券商/手动执行接口\n\n### E. 中心控制层（OpenClaw）\n职责：控制塔与调度层，而非底层撮合引擎。\n\n适合承担：\n- 定时任务调度\n- 数据健康检查\n- 策略对比和研究汇总\n- 报告推送\n- 运维与异常报警\n\n## 4. 当前 workspace 分层建议\n\n### 主系统（唯一生产主线）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"# 个人量化投资系统架构说明（v1）\n\n## 1. 目标\n构建一个可持续运行的个人量化投资系统，覆盖：\n- 数据更新\n- 策略研发\n- 统一回测评估\n- 风控与仓位管理\n- 盘前/盘后自动化\n- 报告与复盘\n- 面向实盘决策的输出\n\n## 2. 系统定位\n当前建议将 `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system` 作为唯一主系统（生产主线）。\n其他目录作为上游数据层或策略实验层，不直接承担生产执行职责。\n\n## 3. 四层一中心架构\n\n### A. 数据层\n职责：标准化提供行情、基本面、指数、持仓、成交等数据。\n\n建议上游来源：\n- `quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis`\n- 同花顺导出/同步脚本\n- Tushare / AkShare\n- 后续可接入 QuestDB\n\n建议统一核心数据对象：\n- `daily_price`\n- `daily_basic`\n- `index_daily`\n- `financial_indicator`\n- `holdings_snapshot`\n- `trades_snapshot`\n- `benchmark_series`\n\n字段标准：\n- 股票代码统一 `ts_code`\n- 日期统一 `trade_date`\n- 行情统一 `open/high/low/close/vol/amount`\n- 基本面统一 `turnover_rate/market_cap/circ_mv/...`\n\n### B. 策略研发层\n职责：策略原型开发、参数试验、回测验证。\n\n建议纳入：\n- `quant_projects/jq_strategies`\n- `quant_projects/qlib`\n- `RD-Agent`\n- 各类 `backtest_*` 脚本\n\n原则：\n- 研发层不直接对接生产执行\n- 所有策略统一输出 `signal` 结构\n\n推荐 signal 结构：\n```csv\ntrade_date,ts_code,signal_type,target_weight,score,strategy_id,comment\n2026-03-09,000001.SZ,BUY,0.10,0.82,smallcap_chip_v4_2,alpha_recover\n```\n\n### C. 风控与组合层\n职责：统一管理仓位、风险、预算与多策略合成。\n\n应独立成模块，不再散落在各策略内部。建议包含：\n- `breadth_guard`\n- `liquidity_guard`\n- `position_sizer`\n- `risk_engine`\n- `blacklist`\n- `portfolio_allocator`\n\n核心原则：\n> 策略负责提出“买什么”，风控负责决定“能不能买、买多少”。\n\n### D. 执行与报告层\n职责：将 signal 转化为订单建议，将系统状态转化为报告和面板。\n\n建议保留在主系统内：\n- 盘前 precheck\n- 订单建议单\n- 净额合并\n- dashboard 生成\n- 每日审计\n- 飞书推送\n- 后续券商/手动执行接口\n\n### E. 中心控制层（OpenClaw）\n职责：控制塔与调度层，而非底层撮合引擎。\n\n适合承担：\n- 定时任务调度\n- 数据健康检查\n- 策略对比和研究汇总\n- 报告推送\n- 运维与异常报警\n\n## 4. 当前 workspace 分层建议\n\n### 主系统（唯一生产主线）","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773926733152}}
{"type":"message","id":"76a43778","parentId":"961c4dc1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:25:50.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me summarize what I know about the integration:\n\n1. **Data dependency**: The personal-a-share-research-system uses `daily_stock_analysis` as a data source:\n   - `index_000852_SH.csv`, `index_000300_SH.csv` (benchmark data)\n   - `stock_basic.csv` (stock list)\n   - `.env.tushare` for Tushare API credentials\n\n2. **Skill integration**: The `daily_stock_analysis` has a SKILL.md with `stock_analyzer` skill, but the personal-a-share-research-system doesn't have its own SKILL.md that references it.\n   \n3. **Script-level integration**: Several scripts directly reference paths in the daily_stock_analysis directory, though some imports like `StockTrendAnalyzer` from `src.stock_analyzer` are failing—the system architecture recommends treating daily_stock_analysis as a data upstream source rather than integrating its skills directly.\n\n4. **Execution layer**: The personal-a-share-research-system uses `.env.tushare` from daily_stock_analysis for Tushare credentials, but the integration is limited to script-level hardcoded paths with no unified data access layer, meaning there's no SKILL.md binding, no unified config, and the analyzer_service isn't systematically wired into the main system. The skill sits in its own project but isn't actually connected to the execution flow.","thinkingSignature":"4d26a74327dea41c9dcf3626945ae832c42fdab0468be4a91041391ff9ea49d8"},{"type":"text","text":"情况如下：\n\n---\n\n## 融合现状\n\n**融合度：部分连接（数据层）**\n\n`daily_stock_analysis` 被当作**数据源**和 **skill 技能库**使用，但和主量化系统（`personal-a-share-research-system`）之间是**散点引用，没有统一封装**。\n\n### 已融合的部分\n\n| 类别 | 具体情况 |\n|---|---|\n| 基准指数数据 | 2 个脚本读取 `index_000852_SH.csv`、`index_000300_SH.csv` |\n| 股票基础数据 | 多个脚本读取 `stock_basic.csv` |\n| Tushare 凭证 | 大量 `run_*.sh` 脚本读取 `.env.tushare` |\n| stock_analyzer skill | 存在 SKILL.md，但只在 2 个技术Replay脚本中直接 import |\n\n### 未融合的部分\n\n| 类别 | 现状 |\n|---|---|\n| 策略研发层 | `daily_stock_analysis` 的 `analyzer_service` 没有接入主系统信号管线 |\n| 风控层 | 没有使用 `stock_analyzer` 的风控/情绪功能 |\n| 报告层 | dashboard 生成依赖 data 层，但 skill 层没串进来 |\n| 定时任务层 | cron 盘前/盘后脚本没有调用 `stock_analyzer` skill |\n| SKILL.md 绑定 | `stock_analyzer` skill 存在但没有被 OpenClaw 主动调度 |\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n`daily_stock_analysis` 目前主要作为**数据目录 + 分析工具**存在，主系统是**读取它的数据**，但没有真正用它的分析能力。\n\n需要我把它更深地接进来吗？比如把 `analyzer_service` 的个股分析能力接入盘前/盘中检查链？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34244,"output":638,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773926733170}}
{"type":"message","id":"26554b00","parentId":"76a43778","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:25:59.681Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<active-task-guard>\nSource: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\nStatus: active\nUse this only as the recovery rail for the current multi-step task.\nIf the user's latest message is a continuation, continue from Current, update ACTIVE_TASK.md after each minimum deliverable, and immediately promote the next item.\nIf the user's latest message is clearly unrelated, do not force this task.\n\nGoal:\n- 量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划，按连续执行清单逐项推进到可验证产物\n\nAcceptance:\n- 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链，并有可验证证据\n- 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版落地并产出结果文件\n- 下午自动重跑强制刷新链具备机器可检验能力\n- 多源实时宽度兜底落地\n\nCurrent:\n- 梳理 corrected 账本与原始账本的安全切换策略\n\nNext:\n- 若 runtime 条件改善，再重新评估是否安全切换主链入口\n- 若主链入口切换稳定，再评估 corrected 账本是否需要安全替换原始账本\n- 把 guarded wrapper 入口约束写入持续检查链\n\nRecent Evidence:\n- 120a8a2 feat: add quant p0/p1 bug backlog and audit\n- ef9ac9b feat: add scheduled tester guard for quant consistency\n- 4178356 feat: add paper account guard validation\n- 9647be1 fix: block paper profile chain before account write under halt\n\nIntegrity Warnings:\n- None\n\nBlockers:\n- 当前 runtime 仍为 halt，无法用真实盘中恢复路径完成“恢复买入”动态验证；当前项先聚焦把 Python 写账户前阻断继续下沉，并用静态脚本与检查报告验收\n</active-task-guard>\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548bd8aaa4a0c31be7150990e84\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 21:25 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b548bd8aaa4a0c31be7150990e84]\nou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7: 好的"}],"timestamp":1773926759680}}
