{"type":"message","id":"1a77a500","parentId":"f4a79a62","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:28:07.398Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_oj3p0yprifya_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md\n\nStatus: active\nPriority: P1\nStarted: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\nUpdated: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\nWorkspace: /absolute/path\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: original user instruction\nResume Entry: first file/report/command to reopen\n\n## Goal\n- One-sentence definition of the task to finish\n\n## Acceptance\n- Deliverable or proof 1\n- Deliverable or proof 2\n\n## Current\n- Exactly one item being executed now\n\n## Next\n- Next pending item\n- Next pending item after that\n\n## Completed\n- [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM] Finished item + proof\n\n## Evidence\n- /absolute/path/to/file\n- command + key output summary\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"# ACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md\n\nStatus: active\nPriority: P1\nStarted: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\nUpdated: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\nWorkspace: /absolute/path\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: original user instruction\nResume Entry: first file/report/command to reopen\n\n## Goal\n- One-sentence definition of the task to finish\n\n## Acceptance\n- Deliverable or proof 1\n- Deliverable or proof 2\n\n## Current\n- Exactly one item being executed now\n\n## Next\n- Next pending item\n- Next pending item after that\n\n## Completed\n- [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM] Finished item + proof\n\n## Evidence\n- /absolute/path/to/file\n- command + key output summary\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773926887385}}
{"type":"message","id":"08b7970e","parentId":"1a77a500","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:28:23.324Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create the ACTIVE_TASK.md for this three-layer integration work. Let me also create a sub-task list for tracking.\n\nThe three layers:\n1. Layer 1: Enhance stock_level_realtime_gate.py with analyzer_service sentiment + advice (个股实时门禁增强)\n2. Layer 2: Connect perform_market_review() to premarket precheck chain (盘前检查链接入大盘复盘)\n3. Layer 3: Connect analyze_stock() to intraday monitoring + close review (盘中值班/盘后审计接入个股分析)\n\nLet me create the ACTIVE_TASK first.","thinkingSignature":"371b47de50a9bfa7f8af462b8f81925bd37497515571ddbcb4377519d5f995e0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fs5sq999zv3i_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","content":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-19 21:27\nUpdated: 2026-03-19 21:27\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 把 daily_stock_analysis 深融合到量化系统，三层全部落地\n\n## Goal\n- 将 daily_stock_analysis 的 analyzer_service 深融合进量化系统三层链路\n\n## Acceptance\n- 第一层：个股实时门禁可调用 analyze_stock 的情绪得分/操作建议作为否决票，并产出可验证报告\n- 第二层：盘前检查链接入 perform_market_review 大盘复盘结果，作为整体风险参考字段\n- 第三层：盘中值班或盘后审计可调用 analyze_stocks 对持仓/买入标的出分析报告\n\n## Current\n- 第一层：增强 stock_level_realtime_gate.py，对候选股调用 analyzer_service.analyze_stock，将情绪得分<阈值或操作建议为负面纳入否决票\n\n## Next\n- 第二层：盘前 precheck 起量前调用 perform_market_review()，将大盘情绪写入 precheck 结果 JSON 的新增字段\n- 第三层：在盘中值班 cron 或盘后审计中调用 analyze_stocks 对持仓标的抽检出报告\n- 三层全部完成后输出融合进度报告并 commit\n\n## Completed\n\n## Evidence\n\n## Blockers\n- runtime halt 不影响第一/二层（均可在盘后/非交易时段静态验证）\n\n## Rules\n- Current 必须包含唯一一项正在执行的项目。\n- 完成 Current 后，将其移到 Completed，在 Evidence 下添加证据，然后将 Next 的第一项提升为 Current。\n- 优先一次性重写整个文件，而不是链式多次部分编辑。\n- 每次写入后，读取文件回来并验证 Current、Next 和 Completed 状态，然后再报告新状态。\n- 只有在阻断真实且具体时才设置 Status: blocked。\n- 只有在 Acceptance 全部满足时才设置 Status: done。\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41276,"output":571,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773926887399}}
