{"type":"message","id":"14787a7d","parentId":"efdaac9c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:28:48.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. Let me build the enhanced `stock_level_realtime_gate.py` that:\n\n1. Tries to import `analyzer_service` from the `daily_stock_analysis` path\n2. For each candidate that passes the price check, additionally calls `analyze_stock` to get sentiment/advice\n3. Uses sentiment score and operation advice as additional veto criteria\n\nThe key thresholds based on the SKILL.md:\n- sentiment_score: range likely 0-100 or 0-1, need to check\n- operation_advice: categories are \"买入\", \"加仓\", \"持有\", \"观望\", \"减仓\", \"卖出\"\n\n\n- Any \"减仓\" or \"卖出\" advice should be blocked\n\nI need to examine the actual return format to calibrate the thresholds properly.","thinkingSignature":"60efacc34c8f2042ee4f463d5c0a6fdb124af67f6ae69824993b63abf266ab43"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mtlab9jw0yj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '26,70p' ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/analyzer_service.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43863,"output":215,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773926921929}}
{"type":"message","id":"dbd6fe49","parentId":"14787a7d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:28:48.800Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3mtlab9jw0yj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def analyze_stock(\n    stock_code: str,\n    config: Config = None,\n    full_report: bool = False,\n    notifier: Optional[NotificationService] = None\n) -> Optional[AnalysisResult]:\n    \"\"\"\n    分析单只股票\n    \n    Args:\n        stock_code: 股票代码\n        config: 配置对象（可选，默认使用单例）\n        full_report: 是否生成完整报告\n        notifier: 通知服务（可选）\n        \n    Returns:\n        分析结果对象\n    \"\"\"\n    if config is None:\n        config = get_config()\n    \n    # 创建分析流水线\n    pipeline = StockAnalysisPipeline(\n        config=config,\n        query_id=uuid.uuid4().hex,\n        query_source=\"cli\"\n    )\n    \n    # 使用通知服务（如果提供）\n    if notifier:\n        pipeline.notifier = notifier\n    \n    # 根据full_report参数设置报告类型\n    report_type = ReportType.FULL if full_report else ReportType.SIMPLE\n    \n    # 运行单只股票分析\n    result = pipeline.process_single_stock(\n        code=stock_code,\n        skip_analysis=False,\n        single_stock_notify=notifier is not None,\n        report_type=report_type\n    )\n    \n    return result"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"def analyze_stock(\n    stock_code: str,\n    config: Config = None,\n    full_report: bool = False,\n    notifier: Optional[NotificationService] = None\n) -> Optional[AnalysisResult]:\n    \"\"\"\n    分析单只股票\n    \n    Args:\n        stock_code: 股票代码\n        config: 配置对象（可选，默认使用单例）\n        full_report: 是否生成完整报告\n        notifier: 通知服务（可选）\n        \n    Returns:\n        分析结果对象\n    \"\"\"\n    if config is None:\n        config = get_config()\n    \n    # 创建分析流水线\n    pipeline = StockAnalysisPipeline(\n        config=config,\n        query_id=uuid.uuid4().hex,\n        query_source=\"cli\"\n    )\n    \n    # 使用通知服务（如果提供）\n    if notifier:\n        pipeline.notifier = notifier\n    \n    # 根据full_report参数设置报告类型\n    report_type = ReportType.FULL if full_report else ReportType.SIMPLE\n    \n    # 运行单只股票分析\n    result = pipeline.process_single_stock(\n        code=stock_code,\n        skip_analysis=False,\n        single_stock_notify=notifier is not None,\n        report_type=report_type\n    )\n    \n    return result","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773926928787}}
