{"type":"message","id":"439c2244","parentId":"fa9e820b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:29:07.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. The `AnalysisResult` has:\n- `sentiment_score`: Integer (likely 0-100)\n- `operation_advice`: String like \"买入\", \"加仓\", \"持有\", \"观望\", \"减仓\", \"卖出\"\n\nNow let me build the enhanced `stock_level_realtime_gate.py`. I'll:\n\n1. Add sys.path injection to import from `daily_stock_analysis`\n2. Add a function `fetch_analyzer_service_analysis(symbol)` that tries to load and call analyzer_service\n3. For each candidate that passes the quote check, also run the analyzer service check\n4. Block if: sentiment_score is below threshold OR operation_advice is in {减仓, 卖出}\n\n\n5. The call to analyzer_service could be slow, so I'll make it optional and add a `--use-analyzer` flag to control it, wrapping it in a try-except so the gate still functions even if the service isn't available","thinkingSignature":"312ea93e3c10b50a92d7c707828c30dde74a801ab1a25b4b950797f88e15cfb3"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我来写增强版 gate。分两步：先写增强脚本，再写验证报告。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hepfh0bwlnws_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate.py ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44950,"output":289,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773926938327}}
