{"type":"message","id":"9d1bf3d4","parentId":"e6024a7b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:46:12.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The v2 script works. Now let's test without the skip flag to see if the market_review integration works. But as before, the analyzer_service will likely be slow or fail due to data source issues. Let me just test with a timeout.Actually, let me just check if the output JSON has the market_review field we added, and note the behavior. Then I can commit layer 2.","thinkingSignature":"858759eb9ecef4b6b6d4e57114aec34e39cd56e67813521b388f548d87223acf"},{"type":"text","text":"基线跑通。现在测试带 market_review 的版本（analyzer 预计会超时/失败，这是预期行为）：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ct8z7g3hbf6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 scripts/run_premarket_risk_v2.py --date 20260319 2>&1 &\nPID=$!\nsleep 60 && kill $PID 2>/dev/null\nwait $PID 2>/dev/null\necho \"done\"","yieldMs":65000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":75769,"output":208,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100270,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773927967130}}
{"type":"message","id":"301d29d4","parentId":"9d1bf3d4","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:47:12.748Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0ct8z7g3hbf6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"未配置有效的通知渠道，将不发送推送通知\n[Tavily] API Key tvly-dev... 进入冷却 3600s: API 配额已用尽: This request exceeds your plan's set usage limit. Please upgrade your plan or contact support@tavily.com\nTavily 搜索失败: API 配额已用尽: This request exceeds your plan's set usage limit. Please upgrade your plan or contact support@tavily.com，尝试下一个引擎\n{\n  \"premarket_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_premarket_risk_v2_20260319.json\",\n  \"premarket_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_premarket_risk_v2_20260319.md\",\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"score\": 5,\n    \"level\": \"RED\",\n    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n    \"halt_new_buy\": true,\n    \"risk_off\": true,\n    \"hard_stop\": true,\n    \"gross_scale\": 0.3,\n    \"reasons\": [\n      \"ZZ2000单日-2.31% <= -1.50%（指数硬停）\",\n      \"市场宽度0.092 <= 0.250（宽度硬停）\"\n    ],\n    \"raw_reasons\": [\n      \"index_ret_pct(-2.3141) <= -1.5000\",\n      \"market_breadth(0.0920) <= 0.2500\"\n    ],\n    \"market_breadth\": 0.09200438116100766,\n    \"style_snapshot\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"smallcap_index\": \"ZZ2000\",\n      \"broad_index\": \"HS300\",\n      \"short_window\": 5,\n      \"medium_window\": 20,\n      \"short_excess_pct\": -2.8933,\n      \"medium_excess_pct\": -1.2386,\n      \"smallcap_short_return_pct\": -5.1185,\n      \"smallcap_medium_return_pct\": -4.0085,\n      \"broad_short_return_pct\": -2.2252,\n      \"broad_medium_return_pct\": -2.7699,\n      \"smallcap_index_file\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000852_SH.csv\",\n      \"broad_index_file\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000300_SH.csv\",\n      \"source_date_key\": 20260319,\n      \"reason\": \"ok\"\n    },\n    \"runtime_gate\": {\n      \"benchmark_code\": \"ZZ2000\",\n      \"benchmark_ret_pct\": -2.3141,\n      \"index_halt_threshold_pct\": -1.5,\n      \"market_breadth_riskoff_threshold\": 0.35,\n      \"market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold\": 0.25,\n      \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": null,\n      \"strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold\": 0.8,\n      \"style_rotation_riskoff_short_excess_pct\": -1.5,\n      \"style_rotation_riskoff_medium_excess_pct\": -3.0,\n      \"style_rotation_hard_stop_short_excess_pct\": -3.0,\n      \"style_rotation_hard_stop_medium_excess_pct\": -5.0\n    },\n    \"combo\": {\n      \"annual_return_pct\": 63.23,\n      \"max_drawdown_pct\": 22.37,\n      \"sharpe\": 2.312\n    },\n    \"index_ret_pct\": {\n      \"ZZ2000\": -2.314065414265265,\n      \"HS300\": -1.611763471408778,\n      \"ZZ500\": -2.709066403558036\n    },\n    \"date\": \"20260319\",\n    \"market_review\": \"## 2026-03-19 大盘复盘\\n\\n### 一、市场总结\\n今日市场呈现普跌格局，三大指数全线收绿，深市跌幅大于沪市。两市成交额维持在2.1万亿以上，但个股呈现极端分化，下跌家数接近5000家，市场亏钱效应显著。\\n\\n> 📈 上涨 **505** 家 / 下跌 **4955** 家 / 平盘 **19** 家 | 涨停 **38** / 跌停 **14** | 成交额 **21273** 亿\\n\\n### 二、指数点评\\n主要指数集体走弱，形成共振下跌。上证指数失守关键点位，跌幅1.39%；深证成指与创业板指跌幅均超1%，其中科创50指数领跌，跌幅达2.44%，显示科技成长方向承压较重。上证50与沪深300同步下跌，权重股未能起到护盘作用。\\n\\n| 指数 | 最新 | 涨跌幅 | 成交额(亿) |\\n|------|------|--------|-----------|\\n| 上证指数 | 4006.55 | 🔴 -1.39% | 9353 |\\n| 深证成指 | 13901.57 | 🔴 -2.02% | 11757 |\\n| 创业板指 | 3309.10 | 🔴 -1.11% | 5417 |\\n| 科创50 | 1339.03 | 🔴 -2.44% | 620 |\\n| 上证50 | 2916.23 | 🔴 -1.53% | 1364 |\\n| 沪深300 | 4583.25 | 🔴 -1.61% | 5479 |\\n\\n### 三、资金动向\\n两市成交额达21273亿元，量能维持高位但指数下跌，属于“放量下跌”的偏空信号。这表明在当前位置，抛售压力较大，承接资金虽活跃但未能有效托市。涨跌家数比（505:4955）极度失衡，显示资金从多数板块流出，市场情绪偏向恐慌。\\n\\n### 四、热点解读\\n**领涨板块**：油气开采与燃气板块逆市大涨，涨幅超7%与4%。这主要反映了地缘政治紧张或能源供应担忧下的避险与涨价预期，属于典型的防御性/事件驱动型行情。\\n**领跌板块**：白银、钼、镍等小金属板块领跌，跌幅均超6%。这可能是对前期涨幅过大的修正，或反映了市场对全球工业需求前景的担忧，资金从周期性板块撤离。\\n\\n> 🔥 领涨: **油气开采Ⅲ**(+7.21%) | **油气开采Ⅱ**(+7.21%) | **燃气Ⅱ**(+4.28%) | **燃气Ⅲ**(+4.28%) | **卫浴电器**(+3.96%)\\n> 💧 领跌: **白银**(-7.66%) | **钼**(-7.27%) | **镍**(-6.81%) | **贵金属**(-6.48%) | **铅锌**(-6.26%)\\n\\n### 五、后市展望\\n市场放量普跌，短期技术形态走坏，情绪面受到冲击。明日需重点关注上证指数能否在关键支撑位（如4000点整数关口）止跌企稳。若权重板块不能发力，指数有继续向下寻找支撑的可能，操作上应以防守为主。\\n\\n### 六、风险提示\\n1. **情绪扩散风险**：今日普跌格局若延续，可能引发更多止损盘和恐慌性抛售。\\n2. **主线缺失风险**：仅油气板块独强，缺乏有号召力的新主线，市场赚钱效应难以恢复。\\n3. **量价背离风险**：高位放量下跌，需警惕是否为阶段性顶部信号。\\n\\n### 七、策略计划\\n**结论：防守**\\n**仓位建议**：将整体仓位降至5成以下，优先减持高位、破位及跟风下跌的品种。\\n**触发失效条件**：若明日市场出现放量（>2.2万亿）反包阳线，且上涨家数恢复至3000家以上，则防守策略需重新评估，可转为均衡策略。\\n建议仅供参考，不构成投资建议。\",\n    \"market_review_available\": true\n  },\n  \"market_review_available\": true\n}\ndone"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":60054,"aggregated":"未配置有效的通知渠道，将不发送推送通知\n[Tavily] API Key tvly-dev... 进入冷却 3600s: API 配额已用尽: This request exceeds your plan's set usage limit. Please upgrade your plan or contact support@tavily.com\nTavily 搜索失败: API 配额已用尽: This request exceeds your plan's set usage limit. Please upgrade your plan or contact support@tavily.com，尝试下一个引擎\n{\n  \"premarket_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_premarket_risk_v2_20260319.json\",\n  \"premarket_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_premarket_risk_v2_20260319.md\",\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"score\": 5,\n    \"level\": \"RED\",\n    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n    \"halt_new_buy\": true,\n    \"risk_off\": true,\n    \"hard_stop\": true,\n    \"gross_scale\": 0.3,\n    \"reasons\": [\n      \"ZZ2000单日-2.31% <= -1.50%（指数硬停）\",\n      \"市场宽度0.092 <= 0.250（宽度硬停）\"\n    ],\n    \"raw_reasons\": [\n      \"index_ret_pct(-2.3141) <= -1.5000\",\n      \"market_breadth(0.0920) <= 0.2500\"\n    ],\n    \"market_breadth\": 0.09200438116100766,\n    \"style_snapshot\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"smallcap_index\": \"ZZ2000\",\n      \"broad_index\": \"HS300\",\n 