{"type":"message","id":"b2db561e","parentId":"391fdaa4","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:59:25.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the analyzer ran and returned:\n- 德赛西威 (002920)\n- 情绪得分: 29\n- 操作建议: 卖出\n\nBut there were errors:\n- Pytdx connection failed\n- Eastmoney API proxy error\n- Tavily API quota exhausted\n\nThe `core_conclusion` attribute doesn't exist as a direct attribute, it's a method `get_core_conclusion()`. Let me get more details. But actually the core info is already there.\n\nThe sentiment score is 29 which is below the threshold of 40, and the operation advice is \"卖出\" (sell). \n\nSince the data sources are limited right now, let me also try to get some basic market data for this stock using the real-time quote function I already have.","thinkingSignature":"a99f6b1dcc082d6db237716097be702f728e7490cda73a121919257831b30a78"},{"type":"text","text":"\nanalyzer_service 分析结果：\n\n- **德赛西威**（002920）\n- 情绪得分：**29**（低于 40 阈值）\n- 操作建议：**卖出**\n\n不过现在有几个数据源问题（非交易时段正常）：\n- Pytdx 连接失败\n- Eastmoney 代理报错\n- Tavily API 配额用尽\n\n补充一个腾讯实时快照：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yhv3n1ytm59g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request, re\nurl = 'http://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sz002920'\nwith urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=8) as resp:\n    text = resp.read().decode('gbk', errors='ignore')\nm = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\\\"(.*)\\\";', text.strip())\nif m:\n    f = m.group(1).split('~')\n    name = f[1]\n    price = f[3]\n    change_pct = f[32]\n    vol = f[36]\n    amount = f[37]\n    high = f[33]\n    low = f[34]\n    open_p = f[5]\n    prev_close = f[4]\n    pe = f[39]\n    print(f'名称: {name}')\n    print(f'现价: {price}')\n    print(f'涨跌幅: {change_pct}%')\n    print(f'今开: {open_p} / 昨收: {prev_close}')\n    print(f'最高: {high} / 最低: {low}')\n    print(f'成交量: {vol}手')\n    print(f'成交额: {amount}万')\n    print(f'市盈率: {pe}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal",