{"type":"message","id":"46037056","parentId":"98f6b6b2","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:07:09.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The industries.csv is from March 10 - it's 9 days old! This is why the sector heatmap shows 436 sectors up and 61 down - it's using data from March 10, which was apparently a day when most sectors were up.\n\nSo the issue is that the `generate_sector_heatmap.py` script reads from a static local CSV file that hasn't been updated since March 10. It doesn't fetch real-time sector data.\n\nSimilarly, the CTO real data dashboard and stock lens dashboard likely also depend on this stale data.\n\nThe real fix would be to either:\n1. Update the industries.csv with today's data (need a data source)\n2. Modify the heatmap generator to use real-time data from an API\n\n\n3. Check what data sources the CTO dashboard and stock lens are pulling from to see if they're also reading from this outdated CSV or if they have their own connection issues.","thinkingSignature":"0fdcc2ec256f52a9785ccc76649d7b03751fe7f810c8e9510c26f1f7a95d8abe"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根本原因了：\n\n`data/industries.csv` 是 **3月10日**的数据（9天前），热力图用的是这个旧文件，所以显示 436 涨 61 跌。\n\n这不是面板生成脚本的问题，是**数据源没有今日实时板块数据**。同花顺的板块数据目前没有接入自动化更新链路。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n03wnqecn2mr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"industries\\|板块\\|sector\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_sector_heatmap.py | head -20; echo \"---\"; grep -rn \"industries\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_cto_real_data_dashboard.py | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97128,"output":359,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773929218258}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a762f47","parentId":"46037056","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:07:09.620Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n03wnqecn2mr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2:板块热力图生成器 — 基于本地行业数据\n3:Usage: python3 generate_sector_heatmap.py\n5:数据来源: data/industries.csv (需定期更新)\n16:    \"\"\"从本地 CSV 加载行业板块数据\"\"\"\n27:                \"code\": str(row.get(\"板块代码\", \"\")),\n28:                \"name\": str(row.get(\"板块名称\", \"\")),\n41:def generate_heatmap_html(sectors: List[Dict], output_path: Path) -> str:\n44:    sorted_sectors = sorted(sectors, key=lambda x: x.get(\"change_pct\", 0), reverse=True)\n70:    <title>A股板块热力图</title>\n95:        .sector {\n104:        .sector:hover {\n108:        .sector-name {\n113:        .sector-pct {\n150:    <h1>A股板块热力图</h1>\n156:            <div class=\"stat-label\">上涨板块</div>\n160:            <div class=\"stat-label\">下跌板块</div>\n164:            <div class=\"stat-label\">总板块数</div>\n174:        document.querySelectorAll('.sector').forEach(el => {\n187:    up_count = sum(1 for s in sorted_sectors if s.get(\"change_pct\", 0) > 0)\n188:    down_count = sum(1 for s in sorted_sectors if s.get(\"change_pct\", 0) < 0)\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":18,"aggregated":"2:板块热力图生成器 — 基于本地行业数据\n3:Usage: python3 generate_sector_heatmap.py\n5:数据来源: data/industries.csv (需定期更新)\n16:    \"\"\"从本地 CSV 加载行业板块数据\"\"\"\n27:                \"code\": str(row.get(\"板块代码\", \"\")),\n28:                \"name\": str(row.get(\"板块名称\", \"\")),\n41:def generate_heatmap_html(sectors: List[Dict], output_path: Path) -> str:\n44:    sorted_sectors = sorted(sectors, key=lambda x: x.get(\"change_pct\", 0), reverse=True)\n70:    <title>A股板块热力图</title>\n95:        .sector {\n104:        .sector:hover {\n108:        .sector-name {\n113:        .sector-pct {\n150:    <h1>A股板块热力图</h1>\n156:            <div class=\"stat-label\">上涨板块</div>\n160:            <div class=\"stat-label\">下跌板块</di