{"type":"message","id":"2a4101ba","parentId":"9d3772e8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:07:38.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The stock lens dashboard reads from:1. `paper_{profile}_account_v1_latest.json` - the account data (this should be fresh)\n2. `paper_{profile}_portfolio_positions_latest.csv` - positions (should be fresh)3. `paper_{profile}_stock_analysis_overlay_*.json` - the stock analysis overlay (may be stale)4. `today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json` - today's strategy reportThe issue with CTO dashboard and stock lens is that they depend on the sector heatmap which uses the 9-day-old industries.csv.\n\nLet me check the `today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json` to see if it's fresh, and then understand what the actual problem is with the stock lens.\n\n\nI need to regenerate the sector heatmap from a live data source like akshare to fix the stale data issue, then push the updated dashboards to Feishu.","thinkingSignature":"fcd8ddb31442e7637684beccb6d9993ed1075d4735cebcd6eb84a3ba746ca4ff"},{"type":"text","text":"\n问题清楚了，整条数据链路是：\n\n```\nindustries.csv（3月10日！）→ generate_sector_heatmap.py → sector_heatmap_summary.json → CTO面板 / 热力图\n```\n\n CTO 面板和热力图都依赖这个 9 天前的 CSV，所以数据全是错的。\n\n我来用 akshare 拉今日真实板块数据，重新生成：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5y5169rdnzll_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 -c \"\nimport akshare as ak\n# 获取板块实时涨跌\ndf = ak.stock_sector_spot(indicator='涨幅')\nprint('columns:', df.columns.tolist())\nprint('shape:', df.shape)\nprint(df.head(5).to_string())\n\" 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99028,"output":373,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123694,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773929248086}}
