{"type":"message","id":"91bcc61b","parentId":"21882890","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:22:04.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to rollback/close all three profiles: aggressive (already done), balanced, and defensive. Let me get the current prices and calculate the corrections for balanced and defensive portfolios.\n\nFrom the latest prices (from Tencent):- 航天电器 (sz002025): 60.79\n- 北斗星通 (sz002151): 44.60- 创新医疗 (sz002173): 28.42\n\nBalanced positions:- 航天电器: 1000 shares @ 58.0713- 北斗星通: 1300 shares @ 45.5403- 创新医疗: 4000 shares @ 29.9064Defensive positions:\n\n\n- 北斗星通: 600 shares @ 45.6604\n- 创新医疗: 2600 shares @ 29.9564\n\nNow I'm calculating the P&L for each position by comparing the current price to the cost basis.","thinkingSignature":"2faa590c4764b2ecb1aa784534aa48d4c0ed75ddd7a0fc689be06dccb45b6f3a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bf703gksspte_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\n# 当前股价\nprices = {'002025.SZ': 60.79, '002151.SZ': 44.60, '002173.SZ': 28.42}\n\n# Balanced 持仓\nbal = [\n    {'code':'002025.SZ','shares':1000,'buy':58.0713},\n    {'code':'002151.SZ','shares':1300,'buy':45.5403},\n    {'code':'002173.SZ','shares':4000,'buy':29.9064},\n]\nbal_cash = 763100.54\nbal_pnl = 0\nfor p in bal:\n    cur = prices[p['code']]\n    cost = p['buy'] * p['shares']\n    proceeds = cur * p['shares']\n    fee = proceeds * 0.000085 + max(5, proceeds * 0.000005)\n    pnl = proceeds - cost - fee\n    bal_pnl += pnl\n    print(f\\\"Balanced {p['code']}: 卖出{p['shares']}@{cur}, 盈亏={pnl:+.2f}\\\")\nprint(f'Balanced 总盈亏: {bal_pnl:+.2f}')\nprint(f'Balanced 新现金: {bal_cash + bal_pnl:,.2f}')\nprint()\n\n# Defensive 持仓\ndefs = [\n    {'code':'002151.SZ','shares':600,'buy':45.6604},\n    {'code':'002173.SZ','shares':2600,'buy':29.9564},\n]\ndef_cash = 894717.01\ndef_pnl = 0\nfor p in defs:\n    cur = prices[p['code']]\n    cost = p['buy'] * p['shares']\n    proceeds = cur * p['shares']\n    fee = proceeds * 0.000085 + max(5, proceeds * 0.000005)\n    pnl = proceeds - cost - fee\n    def_pnl += pnl\n    print(f\\\"Defensive {p['code']}: 卖出{p['shares']}@{cur}, 盈亏={pnl:+.2f}\\\")\nprint(f'Defensive 总盈亏: {def_pnl:+.2f}')\nprint(f'Defensive 新现金: {def_cash + def_pnl:,.2f}')\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80,"output":722,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":131146,"totalTokens":131948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773930102183}}
{"type":"message","id":"33499c52","parentId":"91bcc61b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:22:04.452Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bf703gksspte_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Balanced 002025.SZ: 卖出1000@60.79, 盈亏=+2708.53\nBalanced 002151.SZ: 卖出1300@44.6, 盈亏=-1232.32\nBalanced 002173.SZ: 卖出4000@28.42, 盈亏=-5960.26\nBalanced 总盈亏: -4484.05\nBalanced 新现金: 758,616.49\n\nDefensive 002151.SZ: 卖出600@44.6, 盈亏=-643.51\nDefensive 002173.SZ: 卖出2600@28.42, 盈亏=-4005.92\nDefensive 总盈亏: -4649.44\nDefensive 新现金: 890,067.57"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"Balanced 002025.SZ: 卖出1000@60.79, 盈亏=+2708.53\nBalanced 002151.SZ: 卖出1300@44.6, 盈亏=-1232.32\nBalanced 002173.SZ: 卖出4000@28.42, 盈亏=-5960.26\nBalanced 总盈亏: -4484.05\nBalanced 新现金: 758,616.49\n\nDefensive 002151.SZ: 卖出600@44.6, 盈亏=-643.51\nDefensive 002173.SZ: 卖出2600@28.42, 盈亏=-4005.92\nDefensive 总盈亏: -4649.44\nDefensive 新现金: 890,067.57","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773930124442}}
{"type":"message","id":"fece1d03","parentId":"33499c52","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:22:31.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me execute the rollback for both Balanced and Defensive portfolios. I need to:1. Update journal CSV (append SELL rows)2. Clear positions CSV (both regular and _cn versions)3. Update account JSON (both dated and latest)4. Update corrected account JSON if it exists\n\nLet me write a comprehensive script.","thinkingSignature":"b064a1e3e4a356e1a4e46567139558211afaf327b0c1024ea60dbe31c1d142cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1vx56l8xmv8v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"REPORT=~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports\n\n# === Balanced ===\npython3 -c \"\nimport csv, json\n\nREPORT = '$REPORT'\nprices = {'002025.SZ': 60.79, '002151.SZ': 44.60, '002173.SZ': 28.42}\n\nbal_data = [\n    {'code':'002025.SZ','shares':1000,'buy':58.0713,'fee':60.79*1000*0.000085+5},\n    {'code':'002151.SZ','shares':1300,'buy':45.5403,'fee':44.60*1300*0.000085+5},\n    {'code':'002173.SZ','shares':4000,'buy':29.9064,'fee':28.42*4000*0.000085+5},\n]\n\n# 1. 追加 SELL 到 journal\nnew_rows = []\nfor p in bal_data:\n    proceeds = prices[p['code']] * p['shares']\n    cost = p['buy'] * p['shares']\n    fee = proceeds * 0.000085 + max(5, proceeds * 0.000005)\n    pnl = proceeds - cost - fee\n    new_rows.append({\n        'date': '2026-03-19',\n        'strategy_id': 'paper_trading_balanced_v1',\n        'action': 'SELL',\n        'ts_code': p['code'],\n        'price': prices[p['code']],\n        'shares': p['shares'],\n        'weight_before': '', 'weight_after': '',\n        'signal_reason': 'rollback_corrected',\n        'risk_reason': '',\n        'exit_type': 'market',\n        'exit_reason': '盘中平仓止损（系统决定撤销早盘错误买入）',\n        'fee': round(fee, 2),\n        'slippage': 0,\n        'pnl_day': round(pnl, 2),\n        'pnl_total': round(pnl, 2),\n        'drawdown': 0,\n        'notes': f'corrected_buy_entry={p[\\\"code\\\"]}@{p[\\\"buy\\\"]};rollback=true'\n    })\n\njournal_path = f'{REPORT}/paper_balanced_trading_journal_20260319.csv'\ntry:\n    with open(journal_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        existing = len(list(csv.DictReader(f)))\nexcept:\n    existing = 0\n\nwith open(journal_path, 'a', encoding='utf-8', newline='') as f:\n    writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=list(new_rows[0].keys()))\n    writer.writerows(new_rows)\nprint(f'Balanced journal 追加完成（原有{existing}行，新增3行）')\n\n# 2. 清空 positions\nfor fname in ['paper_balanced_portfolio_positions_latest.csv', 'paper_balanced_portfolio_positions_latest_cn.csv']:\n    p = f'{REPORT}/{fname}'\n    with open(p, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        if 'cn' in fname:\n            f.write('股票代码,股票名称,持仓数量,成本价,最新价,市值,浮亏,浮亏比例\\n')\n        else:\n            f.write('symbol,asset_type,name,quantity,cost_price,last_price,market_value,unrealized_pnl,unrealized_pnl_pct\\n')\nprint('Balanced positions 清空完成')\n\n# 3. 更新账户 JSON\nbal_cash = 763100.54\nbal_pnl = sum(prices[p['code']]*p['shares'] - p['buy']*p['shares'] for p in bal_data)\ntotal_fee = sum(prices[p['code']]*p['shares']*0.000085 + max(5, prices[p['code']]*p['shares']*0.000005) for p in bal_data)\nnet_pnl = bal_pnl - total_fee\n\nfor fname in ['paper_balanced_account_v1_20260319.json', 'paper_balanced_account_v1_latest.json', 'paper_balanced_account_v1_20260319_corrected.json']:\n    p = f'{REPORT}/{fname}'\n    if not __import__('pathlib').Path(p).exists():\n        continue\n    with open(p, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        acct = json.load(f)\n    acct['cash'] = round(bal_cash + net_pnl, 2)\n    acct['market_value'] = 0\n    acct['nav'] = round(bal_cash + net_pnl, 2)\n    acct['position_count'] = 0\n    acct['today_buy_count'] = 0\n    acct['today_sell_count'] = 3\n    acct['rollback_applied'] = True\n    with open(p, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        json.dump(acct, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(f'{fname} 更新完成，nav={acct[\\\"nav\\\"]:,.2f}')\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106220,"output":1206,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131719,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773930124455}}
