{"type":"message","id":"f2620b46","parentId":"f8aa096e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:27:47.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - individual stocks work fine. Let me try to get sector/industry data through the `ths` data provider in the daily_stock_analysis project, or through the `fund` or `index` APIs. Let me also try the tushare `pro_bar` for sector data.Actually, let me check what module is available in the daily_stock_analysis project that can get sector data. The ths_market_bridge needs thsdata module. Let me check if there's another way.Let me try to use the tushare `index_classify()` or other sector-related APIs.","thinkingSignature":"35ca842cba7c9f97612f8f37b3c3a5bc2bd7cf5f11a26acbcbfd4d4bccfa4d59"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qlocs76s19og_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TUSHARE_TOKEN='fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc' python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\npro = ts.pro_api('fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc')\n\n# 试终止的接口\nfor api_name in ['index_classify','concept_detail','suspend_d','bak_basic']:\n    try:\n        func = getattr(pro, api_name)\n        if api_name == 'index_classify':\n            df = func()\n        elif api_name == 'concept_detail':\n            df = func(ts_code='000852.SH')\n        else:\n            df = func(trade_date='20260319')\n        print(f'{api_name}: {df.shape}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{api_name}: {e}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110912,"output":368,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773930456522}}
