{"type":"message","id":"684d9280","parentId":"0986e76a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:28:21.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's an `industry` field in `bak_basic`. But it only has name and industry, not price/change data. I need to join with daily data to get sector-level changes. Let me try to get sector-level performance data directly from Tushare Pro, or use the `index_classify` data plus stock prices.Actually, a more efficient approach would be:\n1. Get all stocks' daily pct_chg from `pro.daily(trade_date='20260319')`\n2. Get industry classification from `pro.bak_basic(date='20260319', fields='name,industry')` or `pro.stock_basic()`\n\n\n3. Join them and calculate sector-level performance\n\nThough this approach has scaling issues with 5000+ stocks and requires proper installation of the `thsdata` package. Let me first check if I can use Tushare's sector API directly, or if `ths_market_bridge.py` has an alternative method for fetching sector data without needing that dependency.","thinkingSignature":"a1c0707100e45645cb672ad6e8d8fea63e1e67ecf9b3c3ff1a254637cef18c4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g41xp28tjt4e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TUSHARE_TOKEN='fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc' python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\npro = ts.pro_api('fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc')\n\n# 获取今日全市场日线数据（仅取行业需要的字段）\ndaily = pro.daily(trade_date='20260319', fields='ts_code,pct_chg')\nprint('daily:', daily.shape, daily.head(3))\n\n# 获取行业分类\nind = pro.bak_basic(date='20260319', fields='name,industry')\nprint('industry:', ind.shape)\n\n# 合并\nmerged = ind.merge(daily, left_on='name', right_on='ts_code', how='inner')\nprint('merged:', merged.shape)\nsector = merged.groupby('industry')['pct_chg'].agg(['mean','count']).reset_index()\nsector.columns = ['industry','avg_change_pct','count']\nsector = sector.sort_values('avg_change_pct', ascending=False)\nprint(sector.head(10).to_string())\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110852,"output":512,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773930489118}}
