{"type":"message","id":"d4aa3983","parentId":"cfffeed5","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:29:16.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"AkShare is blocked too by the proxy. Let me try to work with what we have. Let me:\n\n1. Use Tushare Pro to get sector data - but carefully rate-limited\n2. Use the existing `bak_basic` which gives industry for stocks\n3. Batch the daily calls carefully\n\nActually, the most important realization here is that ALL external financial data APIs are blocked in this environment (Eastmoney, AkShare, Pytdx, etc.). Only Tushare Pro works (with a valid token).\n\nThe heatmap needs sector-level data. Let me try a different approach: \n- Get industry classification from `pro.bak_basic` (works, gets 7000 stocks with industry)\n\n\n- Get daily change from `pro.daily` in small batches to avoid rate limits, then aggregate by sector","thinkingSignature":"4bdc8d88c211ce85f8a2c43f8d00e39033d35f4dbe42b2d911d22ac0637ce2b8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_86hx26ojo6jj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TUSHARE_TOKEN='fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc' python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts, time\npro = ts.pro_api('fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc')\n\n# 分批拉每日数据（每批50只）\n# 先拿沪市成分股\ntry:\n    df = pro.stock_basic(exchange='SSE', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name,industry')\n    print('沪市股票:', df.shape, '有行业:', df['industry'].notna().sum())\n    df2 = pro.stock_basic(exchange='SZSE', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name,industry')\n    print('深市股票:', df2.shape, '有行业:', df2['industry'].notna().sum())\n    all_stocks = df.append(df2)\n    print('总计:', len(all_stocks), '有行业:', all_stocks['industry'].notna().sum())\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('stock_basic error:', e)\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":111813,"output":474,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136580,"co