{"type":"message","id":"da0bf9e5","parentId":"32416f57","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:30:40.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got partial data (3789 out of 5191 stocks) due to rate limiting. Let me write a complete script to:1. Get all stocks with industry from stock_basic (one call)\n2. Get daily data in batches with proper rate limiting\n3. Compute sector averages\n4. Generate the heatmap HTMLLet me write this as a complete script that runs as a background task.","thinkingSignature":"62c34502680547b183310af00e3374f73857cc3ab8a7574d5839efa2ea695bec"},{"type":"text","text":"3789只股票的日线数据已拉到。Tushare每分钟限500次，剩余的稍后补拉。现在先生成第一批次数据的热力图：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6rl7wrlpkej4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TUSHARE_TOKEN='fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc' python3 << 'EOF'\nimport tushare as ts, pandas as pd, json, time\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nREPORT = Path.home() / '.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports'\nREPORT.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\npro = ts.pro_api('fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc')\n\nprint('获取行业分类...')\ndf1 = pro.stock_basic(exchange='SSE', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name,industry')\ndf2 = pro.stock_basic(exchange='SZSE', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name,industry')\nstocks = pd.concat([df1, df2], ignore_index=True)\nstocks_with_ind = stocks[stocks['industry'].notna()].copy()\nprint(f'有行业股票: {len(stocks_with_ind)}')\n\nprint('获取日线涨跌（分批）...')\nts_codes = stocks_with_ind['ts_code'].tolist()\nall_daily = []\nbatch_size = 100\nrate_hits = 0\nfor i in range(0, len(ts_codes), batch_size):\n    batch = ts_codes[i:i+batch_size]\n    try:\n        df = pro.daily(ts_code=','.join(batch), trade_date='20260319')\n        if df is not None and not df.empty:\n            all_daily.append(df[['ts_code','pct_chg']])\n        time.sleep(0.2)\n    except Exception as e:\n        if '500' in str(e):\n            rate_hits += 1\n            time.sleep(2)\n\ndaily_all = pd.concat(all_daily, ignore_index=True) if all_daily else pd.DataFrame()\nprint(f'获取日线数据: {len(daily_all)} 条，限流次数: {rate_hits}')\n\n# 合并\nmerged = stocks_with_ind.merge(daily_all, on='ts_code', how='inner')\nprint(f'合并后: {len(merged)} 条')\n\n# 计算行业平均涨跌幅\nsector = merged.groupby('industry').agg(\n    avg_change=('pct_chg', 'mean'),\n    count=('pct_chg', 'count')\n).reset_index()\nsector.columns = ['name', 'change_pct', 'count']\nsector['change_pct'] = sector['change_pct'].round(2)\nsector = sector.sort_values('change_pct', ascending=False)\nsector['up_count'] = merged.groupby('industry').apply(lambda x: (x['pct_chg'] > 0).sum()).values\nsector['down_count'] = merged.groupby('industry').apply(lambda x: (x['pct_chg'] < 0).sum()).values\n\n# 取领涨领跌股\nleader_map = merged.loc[merged.groupby('industry')['pct_chg'].idxmax()][['industry','name','pct_chg']].set_index('industry')\n\ndef get_leader(ind):\n    if ind in leader_map.index:\n        row = leader_map.loc[ind]\n        return row['name'], row['pct_chg']\n    return '-', 0.0\n\nsector['leader'] = sector['name'].apply(lambda x: get_leader(x)[0])\nsector['leader_pct'] = sector['name'].apply(lambda x: get_leader(x)[1])\n\nprint(f'板块数: {len(sector)}')\nprint(sector.head(5).to_string())\n\n# 保存 JSON summary\nresult = {\n    'generated_at': time.strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S'),\n    'total_sectors': len(sector),\n    'up_count': int((sector['change_pct'] > 0).sum()),\n    'down_count': int((sector['change_pct'] < 0).sum()),\n    'top_gainers': [\n        {'name': r['name'], 'change_pct': r['change_pct'], 'count': int(r['count'])}\n        for _, r in sector.head(5).iterrows()\n    ],\n    'top_losers': [\n        {'name': r['name'], 'change_pct': r['change_pct'], 'count': int(r['count'])}\n        for _, r in sector.tail(5).iterrows()\n    ],\n    'all_sectors': sector.to_dict('records'),\n    'data_source': 'tushare_pro_bak_basic+daily',\n    'stocks_merged': len(merged)\n}\nsummary_path = REPORT / 'sector_heatmap_summary.json'\nsummary_path.write_text(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\nprint(f'\\n保存到: {summary_path}')\n\n# 重新生成 HTML\nhtml = f\"\"\"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><title>A股板块热力图 2026-03-19</title>\n<style>\nbody{{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;margin:20px;background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff}}\nh1{{color:#fff}}\n.stat{{display:flex;gap:30px;margin:20px 0}}\n.stat div{{background:#16213e;padding:15px 25px;border-radius:8px;text-align:center}}\n.stat .num{{font-size:2em;font-weight:bold;color:#00d4ff}}\n.meta{{color:#888;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:20px}}\ntable{{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:20px}}\nth{{background:#0f3460;padding:10px;text-align:left}}\ntd{{padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #222}}\ntr:hover{{background:#1f4068}}\n.gainer{{color:#ff6b6b}}\n.loser{{color:#4ecdc4}}\n</style></head><body>\n<h1>A股板块热力图 <span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#888\">2026-03-19（收盘）</span></h1>\n<div class=\"meta\">数据来源：Tushare Pro（{len(merged)}只股票聚合） | 生成时间：{time.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}</div>\n<div class=\"stat\">\n  <div><div class=\"num\">{result['up_count']}</div>上涨板块</div>\n  <div><div class=\"num\">{result['down_count']}</div>下跌板块</div>\n  <div><div class=\"num\">{result['total_sectors']}</div>总板块数</div>\n</div>\n<table><thead><tr><th>板块</th><th>平均涨跌幅</th><th>股票数</th><th>上涨家</th><th>下跌家</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n\"\"\"\nfor _, r in sector.iterrows():\n    cls = 'gainer' if r['change_pct'] > 0 else 'loser'\n    sign = '+' if r['change_pct'] > 0 else ''\n    html += f\"<tr><td>{r['name']}</td><td class='{cls}'>{sign}{r['change_pct']}%</td><td>{r['count']}</td><td>{r['up_count']}</td><td>{r['down_count']}</td></tr>\\n\"\nhtml += \"</tbody></table></body></html>\"\n\nhtml_path = REPORT / 'sector_heatmap_latest.html'\nhtml_path.write_text(html, encoding='utf-8')\nprint(f'热力图HTML保存到: {html_path}')\nEOF\n","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-