{"type":"message","id":"aa4bce36","parentId":"862a6a5d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:32:51.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that there's already a `prewrite_paper_guard` being called at line 21 and `raise RuntimeError` at line 275 if the guard blocks. So there IS a guard in `run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py` already. \n\nBut the \"深层阻断\" (deep blocking) might mean going deeper - i.e., the guard should be called NOT just at the top-level entry of `run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py`, but also at the point where actual account files are being written (lines 949-957 for positions, lines 1012-1013 for accounts).\n \nThe prewrite guard only validates the initial state before execution begins, but the actual writes to account and position files happen later without any validation. \"深层阻断\" means I need to intercept the file write operations themselves and inject the same guard checks there.","thinkingSignature":"9997c506ff8e6296fe0ad07b50898d1f06da8a1eb10cc51671167043a3f6baed"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2efxl3nk6dm8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '840,1040p' ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":113570,"output":238,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773930759696}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4ac5861","parentId":"aa4bce36","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:32:51.616Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2efxl3nk6dm8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"*,\n    report_dir: Path,\n    positions_file: Path,\n    positions_latest_file: Path,\n    nav_curve_file: Path,\n    account_latest_file: Path,\n    history_dir: Path,\n    initial_cash: float,\n    strategy_id: str,\n    profile_slug: str,\n    profile_name: str,\n    start_date_tag: str,\n    today_date_tag: str,\n    pricing_cfg: dict[str, Any],\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    journal_files = sorted(report_dir.glob(journal_glob(profile_slug)))\n    if start_date_tag:\n        journal_files = [path for path in journal_files if extract_date_tag(path) >= start_date_tag]\n    if not journal_files:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"未找到 paper_trading_journal 文件，无法重建模拟盘\")\n\n    holdings: dict[str, HoldingState] = {}\n    curve_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    price_store = PriceStore(history_dir=history_dir)\n    stock_name_map = load_stock_name_map()\n    peak_nav = float(initial_cash)\n    prev_nav = float(initial_cash)\n    cash = float(initial_cash)\n    latest_trade_date_iso = tag_to_iso(extract_date_tag(journal_files[-1]))\n    use_realtime = str(pricing_cfg.get(\"mark_to_market\", \"\")).strip().lower() == \"realtime_then_close\"\n\n    for journal_path in journal_files:\n        date_tag = extract_date_tag(journal_path)\n        trade_date_iso = tag_to_iso(date_tag)\n        df = load_journal(journal_path)\n        buy_count = 0\n        sell_count = 0\n\n        if not df.empty:\n            for _, row in df.iterrows():\n                side = normalize_side(row.get(\"action\", \"\"))\n                qty = abs(parse_int(row.get(\"shares\"), 0))\n                cash = apply_trade(holdings, cash, row, stock_name_map)\n                if side == \"BUY\" and qty > 0:\n                    buy_count += 1\n                elif side == \"SELL\" and qty > 0:\n                    sell_count += 1\n\n        # 补齐所有持仓的 name\n        for sym, h in holdings.items():\n            if not h.name:\n                h.name = stock_name_map.get(sym, \"\")\n\n        day_market_value = 0.0\n        for symbol, holding in holdings.items():\n            price, _ = price_store.mark_price(\n                symbol,\n                trade_date_iso,\n                latest_trade_date_iso,\n                use_realtime=use_realtime,\n            )\n            if price is None or price <= 0:\n                price = holding.cost_price\n            day_market_value += holding_value(holding, price)\n\n        nav = round_cash(cash + day_market_value)\n        day_pnl = round_cash(nav - prev_nav)\n        peak_nav = max(peak_nav, nav)\n        total_pnl = round_cash(nav - initial_cash)\n        drawdown_pct = ((nav / peak_nav) - 1.0) * 100.0 if peak_nav > 0 else 0.0\n        save_daily_metrics(\n            journal_path,\n            df,\n            pnl_day_value=day_pnl,\n            pnl_total_value=total_pnl,\n            drawdown_pct=drawdown_pct,\n        )\n\n        curve_rows.append(\n            {\n                \"date\": trade_date_iso,\n                \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n                \"cash\": round_cash(cash),\n                \"market_value\": round_cash(day_market_value),\n                \"nav\": nav,\n                \"pnl_day\": day_pnl,\n                \"pnl_total\": total_pnl,\n                \"drawdown_pct\": round(drawdown_pct, 2),\n                \"buy_trades\": buy_count,\n                \"sell_trades\": sell_count,\n                \"position_count\": len(holdings),\n            }\n        )\n        prev_nav = nav\n\n    simple_rows, detailed_rows, latest_market_value, realtime_hits = build_positions_rows(\n        holdings=holdings,\n        price_store=price_store,\n        latest_trade_date_iso=latest_trade_date_iso,\n        use_realtime=use_realtime,\n    )\n    latest_nav = round_cash(cash + latest_market_value)\n    latest_peak = max([parse_float(row.get(\"nav\"), initial_cash) for row in curve_rows] + [initial_cash, latest_nav])\n    latest_drawdown = ((latest_nav / latest_peak) - 1.0) * 100.0 if latest_peak > 0 else 0.0\n\n    ensure_parent(nav_curve_file)\n    pd.DataFrame(curve_rows).to_csv(nav_curve_file, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n\n    ensure_parent(positions_file)\n    ensure_parent(positions_latest_file)\n    positions_dated_file = report_path(report_dir, \"positions_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=today_date_tag)\n    pd.DataFrame(simple_rows, columns=POSITION_COLUMNS).to_csv(positions_file, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n    pd.DataFrame(simple_rows, columns=POSITION_COLUMNS).to_csv(positions_dated_file, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n    pd.DataFrame(detailed_rows, columns=DETAILED_POSITION_COLUMNS).to_csv(positions_latest_file, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n\n    positions_dated_cn_file = positions_dated_file.with_name(positions_dated_file.stem + '_cn.csv')\n    positions_latest_cn_file = positions_latest_file.with_name(positions_latest_file.stem + '_cn.csv')\n    write_csv_with_cn_headers(positions_dated_cn_file, detailed_rows, DETAILED_POSITION_COLUMNS, CN_POSITION_HEADER_MAP)\n    write_csv_with_cn_headers(positions_latest_cn_file, detailed_rows, DETAILED_POSITION_COLUMNS, CN_POSITION_HEADER_MAP)\n\n    today_journal = report_path(report_dir, \"journal\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=today_date_tag)\n    today_df = load_journal(today_journal)\n    today_trade_count = int(len(today_df))\n    today_buy_count = int((today_df.get(\"action\", pd.Series([], dtype=str)).astype(str).str.upper() == \"BUY\").sum()) if not today_df.empty else 0\n    today_sell_count = int((today_df.get(\"action\", pd.Series([], dtype=str)).astype(str).str.upper() == \"SELL\").sum()) if not today_df.empty else 0\n    curve_df = pd.DataFrame(curve_rows)\n    today_curve = curve_df[curve_df[\"date_tag\"].astype(str) == str(today_date_tag)].copy()\n    today_pnl = round_cash(parse_float(today_curve[\"pnl_day\"].iloc[-1], 0.0)) if not today_curve.empty else 0.0\n\n    account_payload = {\n        \"date_tag\": today_date_tag,\n        \"trade_date\": tag_to_iso(today_date_tag),\n        \"strategy_id\": strategy_id,\n        \"profile_slug\": profile_slug,\n        \"profile_name\": profile_name,\n        \"start_date_tag\": start_date_tag,\n        \"start_trade_date\": tag_to_iso(start_date_tag) if start_date_tag else \"\",\n        \"initial_cash\": round_cash(initial_cash),\n        \"cash\": round_cash(cash),\n        \"market_value\": latest_market_value,\n        \"nav\": latest_nav,\n        \"total_pnl\": round_cash(latest_nav - initial_cash),\n        \"total_return_pct\": round(((latest_nav / initial_cash) - 1.0) * 100.0, 2) if initial_cash > 0 else 0.0,\n        \"day_pnl\": today_pnl,\n        \"drawdown_pct\": round(latest_drawdown, 2),\n        \"peak_nav\": round_cash(latest_peak),\n        \"position_count\": len(simple_rows),\n        \"today_trade_count\": today_trade_count,\n        \"today_buy_count\": today_buy_count,\n        \"today_sell_count\": today_sell_count,\n        \"realtime_mark_hits\": realtime_hits,\n        \"files\": {\n            \"positions\": str(positions_file),\n            \"positions_latest\": str(positions_latest_file),\n            \"positions_latest_cn\": str(positions_latest_cn_file),\n            \"nav_curve\": str(nav_curve_file),\n            \"today_journal\": str(today_journal),\n        },\n    }\n\n    dated_account_file = report_path(report_dir, \"account_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=today_date_tag)\n    account_payload[\"files\"][\"account_latest\"] = str(account_latest_file)\n    account_payload[\"files\"][\"account_dated\"] = str(dated_account_file)\n    account_payload[\"files\"][\"positions_dated\"] = str(positions_dated_file)\n    guard_report_path = run_prewrite_guard(\n        report_dir=report_dir,\n        profile_slug=profile_slug,\n        today_date_tag=today_date_tag,\n        account_payload=account_payload,\n        account_json_path=account_latest_file,\n    )\n    account_payload[\"files\"][\"prewrite_guard\"] = str(guard_report_path)\n    ensure_parent(account_latest_file)\n    ensure_parent(dated_account_file)\n    _prewrite_guard_or_die(profile=str(locals().get('profile_slug') or locals().get('profile') or 'balanced'), date_tag=str(locals().get('date_tag') or locals().get('trade_date') or __import__('datetime').datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')).replace('-', ''), account_json_path=account_payload[\"files\"][\"prewrite_guard\"])\n    account_latest_file.write_text(json.dumps(account_payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    dated_account_file.write_text(json.dumps(account_payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    return account_payload\n\n\ndef build_summary_markdown(\n    *,\n    date_tag: str,\n    orders_file: Path,\n    account: dict[str, Any],\n    executable_count: int,\n    blocked_count: int,\n) -> str:\n    files = account.get(\"files\", {})\n    return \"\\n\".join(\n        [\n            f\"# 模拟交易摘要 v1（{date_tag}）\",\n            \"\",\n            \"## 今日模拟执行\",\n            f\"- 订单文件：`{orders_file}`\",\n            f\"- 可执行订单数：`{executable_count}`\",\n            f\"- 被拦截订单数：`{blocked_count}`\",\n            f\"- 今日模拟成交：`{account.get('today_trade_count', 0)}`（BUY {account.get('today_buy_count', 0)} / SELL {account.get('today_sell_count', 0)}）\",\n            \"\",\n            \"## 模拟账户\",\n            f\"- 初始资金：`{account.get('initial_cash', 0)}`\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"*,\n    report_dir: Path,\n    positions_file: Path,\n    positions_latest_file: Path,\n    nav_curve_file: Path,\n    account_latest_file: Path,\n    history_dir: Path,\n    initial_cash: float,\n    strategy_id: str,\n    profile_slug: str,\n    profile_name: str,\n    start_date_tag: str,\n    today_date_tag: str,\n    pricing_cfg: dict[str, Any],\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    journal_files = sorted(report_dir.glob(journal_glob(profile_slug)))\n    if start_date_tag:\n        journal_files = [path for path in journal_files if extract_date_tag(path) >= start_date_tag]\n    if not journal_files:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"未找到 paper_trading_journal 文件，无法重建模拟盘\")\n\n    holdings: dict[str, HoldingState] = {}\n    curve_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    price_store = PriceStore(history_dir=history_dir)\n    stock_name_map = load_stock_name_map()\n    peak_nav = float(initial_cash)\n    prev_nav = float(initial_cash)\n    cash = float(initial_cash)\n    latest_trade_date_iso = tag_to_iso(extract_date_tag(journal_files[-1]))\n    use_realtime = str(pricing_cfg.get(\"mark_to_market\", \"\")).strip().lower() == \"realtime_then_close\"\n\n    for journal_path in journal_files:\n        date_tag = extract_date_tag(journal_path)\n        trade_date_iso = tag_to_iso(date_tag)\n        df = load_journal(journal_path)\n        buy_count = 0\n        sell_count = 0\n\n        if not df.empty:\n            for _, row in df.iterrows():\n                side = normalize_side(row.get(\"action\", \"\"))\n                qty = abs(parse_int(row.get(\"shares\"), 0))\n                cash = apply_trade(holdings, cash, row, stock_name_map)\n                if side == \"BUY\" and qty > 0:\n                    buy_count += 1\n                elif side == \"SELL\" and qty > 0:\n                    sell_count += 1\n\n        # 补齐所有持仓的 name\n        for sym, h in holdings.items():\n            if not h.name:\n                h.name = stock_name_map.get(sym, \"\")\n\n        day_market_value = 0.0\n        for symbol, holding in holdings.items():\n            price, _ = price_store.mark_price(\n                symbol,\n                trade_date_iso,\n                latest_trade_date_iso,\n                use_realtime=use_realtime,\n            )\n            if price is None or price <= 0:\n                price = holding.cost_price\n            day_market_value += holding_value(holding, price)\n\n        nav = round_cash(cash + day_market_value)\n        day_pnl = round_cash(nav - prev_nav)\n        peak_nav = max(peak_nav, nav)\n        total_pnl = round_cash(nav - initial_cash)\n        drawdown_pct = ((nav / peak_nav) - 1.0) * 100.0 if peak_nav > 0 else 0.0\n        save_daily_metrics(\n            journal_path,\n            df,\n            pnl_day_value=day_pnl,\n            pnl_total_value=total_pnl,\n            drawdown_pct=drawdown_pct,\n        )\n\n        curve_rows.append(\n            {\n                \"date\": trade_date_iso,\n                \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n                \"cash\": round_cash(cash),\n                \"market_value\": round_cash(day_market_value),\n                \"nav\": nav,\n                \"pnl_day\": day_pnl,\n                \"pnl_total\": total_pnl,\n                \"drawdown_pct\": round(drawdown_pct, 2),\n                \"buy_trades\": buy_count,\n                \"sell_trades\": sell_count,\n                \"position_count\": len(holdings),\n            }\n        )\n        prev_nav = nav\n\n    simple_rows, detailed_rows, latest_market_value, realtime_hits = build_positions_rows(\n        holdings=holdings,\n        price_store=price_store,\n        latest_trade_date_iso=latest_trade_date_iso,\n        use_realtime=use_realtime,\n    )\n    latest_nav = round_cash(cash + latest_market_value)\n    latest_peak = max([parse_float(row.get(\"nav\"), initial_cash) for row in curve_rows] + [initial_cash, latest_nav])\n    latest_drawdown = ((latest_nav / latest_peak) - 1.0) * 100.0 if latest_peak > 0 else 0.0\n\n    ensure_parent(nav_curve_file)\n    pd.DataFrame(curve_rows).to_csv(nav_curve_file, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n\n    ensure_parent(positions_file)\n    ensure_parent(positions_latest_file)\n    positions_dated_file = report