{"type":"message","id":"fb646d2d","parentId":"e0103a8a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:36:59.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, committed. Now let me update the ACTIVE_TASK.md and move to the next item in the queue.","thinkingSignature":"a786e9d1a80b49ebc9058b08abcacc3229606bc2c3055ce08f75b6b85c94d29c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gnsu0u2he2vd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","content":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-19\nUpdated: 2026-03-19 22:37\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\n\n## Goal\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## Acceptance\n- 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链，并有可验证证据\n- 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版落地并产出结果文件\n- 下午自动重跑强制刷新链具备机器可检验能力\n- 多源实时宽度兜底落地\n- 写账户前 Python 深层阻断落地并可验证\n\n## Current\n- 下一批：待从 highest_priority_execution_queue 读取下一个未完成项\n\n## Next\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-03-19] 写账户前 Python 深层阻断：prewrite_paper_guard.py v2 落地\n  - 始终从磁盘重新读取 runtime_risk_state_latest.json（不接受缓存对象）\n  - 直接读 journal 文件检查今日 BUY 条目（halt 时不应有）\n  - halt_new_buy=True + journal 有 BUY → BLOCK (exit 2)\n  - aggressive/balanced/defensive 三账户均验证通过\n\n## Evidence\n- 79068b3 feat: prewrite_paper_guard v2 - always re-read runtime state from disk, check journal BUY entries, deep block before account write\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prewrite_paper_guard.py\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/prewrite_paper_guard_aggressive_20260319.json\n\n## Blockers\n\n## Rules\n- Current 必须包含唯一一项正在执行的项目。\n- 完成 Current 后，将其移到 Completed，在 Evidence 下添加证据，然后将 Next 的第一项提升为 Current。\n- 优先一次性重写整个文件，而不是链式多次部分编辑。\n- 每次写入后，读取文件回来并验证 Current、Next 和 Completed 状态。\n- 只有在阻断真实且具体时才设置 Status: blocked。\n- 只有在 Acceptance 全部满足时才设置 Status: done。\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104441,"output":