{"type":"message","id":"279963fe","parentId":"70f5f065","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:39:47.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No config setting found. So the unified fetcher's `realtime_source_priority` is not being configured in the quant system. \n\nLet me now understand the actual situation:\n\n1. `DataFetcherManager` in `daily_stock_analysis` has THS/TDX in its priority list2. BUT the individual scripts (`intraday_market_gate.py`, `intraday_market_breadth.py`, `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`) are NOT using `DataFetcherManager`3. They call their own specific fetchers directly (Tencent via urllib, AkShare, eFinance)\n\nThe fix needed: Update these entry point scripts to use `DataFetcherManager.get_realtime_quote()` instead of their own specific fetchers.\n\n\nNow I need to plan out the changes. For `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`, I'll need to import `DataFetcherManager` and swap out the `urllib.request` calls to Tencent with `manager.get_realtime_quote()` instead. `intraday_market_gate.py` has the same pattern. For `intraday_market_breadth.py`, it's trickier since it already uses AkShare and eFinance - I'd need to replace those with the unified manager there too.\n\nActually, I realize the `DataFetcherManager` is in the `daily_stock_analysis` project, but these scripts are in `personal-a-share-research-system`. The simpler approach is to use the config-based priority setting via `realtime_source_priority` or `market_data_fetcher_priority` to control which fetcher gets used.\n\nBut I think the most practical path forward is to focus on what the user actually needs: checking if THS/TDX has network access and then modifying `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` to use `DataFetcherManager` with THS/TDX as the priority source.\n\nLet me look at how to actually initialize the `DataFetcherManager` and configure the priority setting.","thinkingSignature":"a5bc2558444107290039cd37bdbd8818f7bd0822a5e4913bab9ea10d971ac1f9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e8af3fxhumrl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '620,730p' ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/data_provider/base.py 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112126,"output":454,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136873,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931175941}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e9e9463","parentId":"279963fe","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:39:47.338Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e8af3fxhumrl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def get_realtime_quote(self, stock_code: str):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情数据（自动故障切换）\n        \n        故障切换策略（按配置的优先级）：\n        1. 美股：使用 YfinanceFetcher.get_realtime_quote()\n        2. EfinanceFetcher.get_realtime_quote()\n        3. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"em\")  - 东财\n        4. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"sina\") - 新浪\n        5. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"tencent\") - 腾讯\n        6. 返回 None（降级兜底）\n        \n        Args:\n            stock_code: 股票代码\n            \n        Returns:\n            UnifiedRealtimeQuote 对象，所有数据源都失败则返回 None\n        \"\"\"\n        # Normalize code (strip SH/SZ prefix etc.)\n        stock_code = normalize_stock_code(stock_code)\n\n        from .realtime_types import get_realtime_circuit_breaker\n        from .akshare_fetcher import _is_us_code\n        from .us_index_mapping import is_us_index_code\n        from src.config import get_config\n\n        config = get_config()\n\n        # 如果实时行情功能被禁用，直接返回 None\n        if not config.enable_realtime_quote:\n            logger.debug(f\"[实时行情] 功能已禁用，跳过 {stock_code}\")\n            return None\n\n        # 美股指数由 YfinanceFetcher 处理（在美股股票检查之前）\n        if is_us_index_code(stock_code):\n            for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                if fetcher.name == \"YfinanceFetcher\":\n                    if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                        try:\n                            quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            if quote is not None:\n                                logger.info(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 成功获取 (来源: yfinance)\")\n                                return quote\n                        except Exception as e:\n                            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 获取失败: {e}\")\n                    break\n            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 无可用数据源\")\n            return None\n\n        # 美股单独处理，使用 YfinanceFetcher\n        if _is_us_code(stock_code):\n            for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                if fetcher.name == \"YfinanceFetcher\":\n                    if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                        try:\n                            quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            if quote is not None:\n                                logger.info(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 成功获取 (来源: yfinance)\")\n                                return quote\n                        except Exception as e:\n                            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 获取失败: {e}\")\n                    break\n            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 无可用数据源\")\n            return None\n        \n        # 获取配置的数据源优先级\n        source_priority = config.realtime_source_priority.split(',')\n        \n        errors = []\n        # primary_quote holds the first successful result; we may supplement\n        # missing fields (volume_ratio, turnover_rate, etc.) from later sources.\n        primary_quote = None\n        \n        for source in source_priority:\n            source = source.strip().lower()\n            \n            try:\n                quote = None\n                \n                if source in (\"ths\", \"ths_market\"):\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"ThsMarketFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n\n                elif source == \"pytdx\":\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"PytdxFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n\n                elif source == \"efinance\":\n                    # 尝试 EfinanceFetcher\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"EfinanceFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n                \n                elif source == \"akshare_em\":\n                    # 尝试 AkshareFetcher 东财数据源\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"AkshareFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code, source=\"em\")\n                            break\n                \n                elif source == \"akshare_sina\":\n                    # 尝试 AkshareFetcher 新浪数据源"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"def get_realtime_quote(self, stock_code: str):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情数据（自动故障切换）\n        \n        故障切换策略（按配置的优先级）：\n        1. 美股：使用 YfinanceFetcher.get_realtime_quote()\n        2. EfinanceFetcher.get_realtime_quote()\n        3. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"em\")  - 东财\n        4. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"sina\") - 新浪\n        5. AkshareFetcher.get_realtime_quote(source=\"tencent\") - 腾讯\n        6. 返回 None（降级兜底）\n        \n        Args:\n            stock_code: 股票代码\n            \n        Returns:\n            UnifiedRealtimeQuote 对象，所有数据源都失败则返回 None\n        \"\"\"\n        # Normalize code (strip SH/SZ prefix etc.)\n        stock_code = normalize_stock_code(stock_code)\n\n        from .realtime_types import get_realtime_circuit_breaker\n        from .akshare_fetcher import _is_us_code\n        from .us_index_mapping import is_us_index_code\n        from src.config import get_config\n\n        config = get_config()\n\n        # 如果实时行情功能被禁用，直接返回 None\n        if not config.enable_realtime_quote:\n            logger.debug(f\"[实时行情] 功能已禁用，跳过 {stock_code}\")\n            return None\n\n        # 美股指数由 YfinanceFetcher 处理（在美股股票检查之前）\n        if is_us_index_code(stock_code):\n            for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                if fetcher.name == \"YfinanceFetcher\":\n                    if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                        try:\n                            quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            if quote is not None:\n                                logger.info(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 成功获取 (来源: yfinance)\")\n                                return quote\n                        except Exception as e:\n                            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 获取失败: {e}\")\n                    break\n            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股指数 {stock_code} 无可用数据源\")\n            return None\n\n        # 美股单独处理，使用 YfinanceFetcher\n        if _is_us_code(stock_code):\n            for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                if fetcher.name == \"YfinanceFetcher\":\n                    if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                        try:\n                            quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            if quote is not None:\n                                logger.info(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 成功获取 (来源: yfinance)\")\n                                return quote\n                        except Exception as e:\n                            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 获取失败: {e}\")\n                    break\n            logger.warning(f\"[实时行情] 美股 {stock_code} 无可用数据源\")\n            return None\n        \n        # 获取配置的数据源优先级\n        source_priority = config.realtime_source_priority.split(',')\n        \n        errors = []\n        # primary_quote holds the first successful result; we may supplement\n        # missing fields (volume_ratio, turnover_rate, etc.) from later sources.\n        primary_quote = None\n        \n        for source in source_priority:\n            source = source.strip().lower()\n            \n            try:\n                quote = None\n                \n                if source in (\"ths\", \"ths_market\"):\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"ThsMarketFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n\n                elif source == \"pytdx\":\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"PytdxFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n\n                elif source == \"efinance\":\n                    # 尝试 EfinanceFetcher\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"EfinanceFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code)\n                            break\n                \n                elif source == \"akshare_em\":\n                    # 尝试 AkshareFetcher 东财数据源\n                    for fetcher in self._fetchers:\n                        if fetcher.name == \"AkshareFetcher\":\n                            if hasattr(fetcher, 'get_realtime_quote'):\n                                quote = fetcher.get_realtime_quote(stock_code, source=\"em\")\n                            break\n                \n                elif source == \"akshare_sina\":\n                    # 尝试 AkshareFetcher 新浪数据源","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931187326}}
{"type":"message","id":"b78e757a","parentId":"3e9e9463","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:40:02.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see how it works. The `DataFetcherManager.get_realtime_quote()` already supports THS and Pytdx as priority sources through the `realtime_source_priority` config. The issue is that `intraday_market_gate.py`, `intraday_market_breadth.py`, and `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` are NOT using this manager - they're calling their own specific fetchers.\n\nThe fix should be to:\n1. Check the current `realtime_source_priority` config\n2. Modify these scripts to use `DataFetcherManager.get_realtime_quote()` instead of their own specific fetchers\n\n\n3. Now I need to verify whether THS/TDX can actually be accessed, since we saw Pytdx was blocked earlier but need to check if THS works.","thinkingSignature":"caec657e424a3f2072ea994ecbed20c5c66449e8c044d38ba26ccb9b9d13a5ae"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_atmk0h6bth3g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"realtime_source_priority\\|enable_realtime_quote\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/src/config.py 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109985,"output":232,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931187344}}
