{"type":"message","id":"48619661","parentId":"8cc92dc4","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:41:12.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to understand how to use `DataFetcherManager` in the entry point scripts. Let me look at how it's instantiated.","thinkingSignature":"a215a5d06d8c61c9db9b27cde6226d5f6ac4c8404f9b576227bbaf38ad6473aa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mdlmcuinkw3l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '332,380p' ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/data_provider/base.py 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109870,"output":83,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931260091}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9db9ba0","parentId":"48619661","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:41:12.992Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mdlmcuinkw3l_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"class DataFetcherManager:\n    \"\"\"\n    数据源策略管理器\n    \n    职责：\n    1. 管理多个数据源（按优先级排序）\n    2. 自动故障切换（Failover）\n    3. 提供统一的数据获取接口\n    \n    切换策略：\n    - 优先使用高优先级数据源\n    - 失败后自动切换到下一个\n    - 所有数据源都失败时抛出异常\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, fetchers: Optional[List[BaseFetcher]] = None):\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化管理器\n        \n        Args:\n            fetchers: 数据源列表（可选，默认按优先级自动创建）\n        \"\"\"\n        self._fetchers: List[BaseFetcher] = []\n        \n        if fetchers:\n            # 按优先级排序\n            self._fetchers = sorted(fetchers, key=lambda f: f.priority)\n        else:\n            # 默认数据源将在首次使用时延迟加载\n            self._init_default_fetchers()\n    \n    def _init_default_fetchers(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化默认数据源列表\n\n        优先级动态调整逻辑：\n        - 如果配置了 TUSHARE_TOKEN：Tushare 优先级提升为 0（最高）\n        - 否则按默认优先级：\n          0. EfinanceFetcher (Priority 0) - 最高优先级\n          1. AkshareFetcher (Priority 1)\n          1. ThsMarketFetcher (Priority 1) - 同花顺桥接\n          2. PytdxFetcher (Priority 2) - 通达信\n          2. TushareFetcher (Priority 2)\n          3. BaostockFetcher (Priority 3)\n          4. YfinanceFetcher (Priority 4)\n        \"\"\"\n        from .efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\n        from .akshare_fetcher import AkshareFetcher\n        from .ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"class DataFetcherManager:\n    \"\"\"\n    数据源策略管理器\n    \n    职责：\n    1. 管理多个数据源（按优先级排序）\n    2. 自动故障切换（Failover）\n    3. 提供统一的数据获取接口\n    \n    切换策略：\n    - 优先使用高优先级数据源\n    - 失败后自动切换到下一个\n    - 所有数据源都失败时抛出异常\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, fetchers: Optional[List[BaseFetcher]] = None):\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化管理器\n        \n        Args:\n            fetchers: 数据源列表（可选，默认按优先级自动创建）\n        \"\"\"\n        self._fetchers: List[BaseFetcher] = []\n        \n        if fetchers:\n            # 按优先级排序\n            self._fetchers = sorted(fetchers, key=lambda f: f.priority)\n        else:\n            # 默认数据源将在首次使用时延迟加载\n            self._init_default_fetchers()\n    \n    def _init_default_fetchers(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化默认数据源列表\n\n        优先级动态调整逻辑：\n        - 如果配置了 TUSHARE_TOKEN：Tushare 优先级提升为 0（最高）\n        - 否则按默认优先级：\n          0. EfinanceFetcher (Priority 0) - 最高优先级\n          1. AkshareFetcher (Priority 1)\n          1. ThsMarketFetcher (Priority 1) - 同花顺桥接\n          2. PytdxFetcher (Priority 2) - 通达信\n          2. TushareFetcher (Priority 2)\n          3. BaostockFetcher (Priority 3)\n          4. YfinanceFetcher (Priority 4)\n        \"\"\"\n        from .efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\n        from .akshare_fetcher import AkshareFetcher\n        from .ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931272979}}
