{"type":"message","id":"89b73d4b","parentId":"9be91a9f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:42:02.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. `normalize_stock_code` handles the conversion. Now let me update `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` to use `DataFetcherManager`. I'll add an optional `--use-unified-fetcher` flag that uses the unified routing with THS/TDX priority.\n\nBut actually, I should just make it use `DataFetcherManager` by default (since that's the proper way), and fall back to the old method if it fails.\n\nLet me now plan the changes to `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`:\n\n1. Add import for `DataFetcherManager` from `daily_stock_analysis.data_provider.base`\n\n\n2. Replace the `fetch_quote()` function with a wrapper that tries `DataFetcherManager.get_realtime_quote()` first, then falls back to the old urllib method if needed\n3. Set `realtime_source_priority` to `ths,pytdx,efinance,akshare_em,tushare` to give THS/TDX priority, which should work for the intraday gate use case\n\nThe key insight is that this approach ensures THS/TDX are tried first through the unified manager, satisfying the routing requirement while maintaining backward compatibility.","thinkingSignature":"fa48cc971ff230011aacacc5f889dfe2fe19c80fb15423015449840df2f99185"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q2vonyfu56ek_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108342,"output":304,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132939,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931308672}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cfb32e3","parentId":"89b73d4b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:42:02.696Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q2vonyfu56ek_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport signal\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nANALYZER_TIMEOUT_SEC = 15  # 单只股票分析超时秒数，超时则视为 unavailable\n\nROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = ROOT / 'research' / 'reports'\nDSA_ROOT = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\n\n# ── thresholds for analyzer_service veto ────────────────────────────────────\nSENTIMENT_SCORE_MIN = 40          # below this → block\nNEGATIVE_ADVICES = {\"减仓\", \"卖出\"}\n\n# ── normalise helpers ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nCODE_FIELDS = ['ts_code', 'ticker', 'symbol', 'code', 'stock_code']\nSIDE_FIELDS = ['side', 'action', 'order_side', 'trade_side', 'signal_side']\nBUY_VALUES = {'buy', 'open_buy', 'long', 'b'}\n\n\ndef normalize_symbol(symbol: str) -> str:\n    s = str(symbol or '').strip().upper()\n    if not s:\n        return s\n    s = s.replace('.', '')\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SH', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SZ', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SH\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SZ\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}', s):\n        return ('sh' if s.startswith('6') else 'sz') + s\n    return s.lower()\n\n\n# ── quote ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\ndef fetch_quote(symbol: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    market_symbol = normalize_symbol(symbol)\n    url = f'http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={market_symbol}'\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=8) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode('gbk', errors='ignore')\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'parse_failed'}\n        f = m.group(1).split('~')\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'field_short'}\n        return {\n            'valid': True,\n            'input_symbol': symbol,\n            'market_symbol': market_symbol,\n            'name': f[1] or '',\n            'price': float(f[3] or 0),\n            'change_pct': float(f[32] or 0),\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': repr(e)}\n\n\n# ── analyzer_service ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\ndef _load_analyzer_service():\n    \"\"\"Lazy-import analyzer_service; return (module, error).\"\"\"\n    if not (DSA_ROOT / 'analyzer_service.py').exists():\n        return None, 'dsa_root_not_found'\n    if str(DSA_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(DSA_ROOT))\n\n[176 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931322683}}
{"type":"message","id":"db492b25","parentId":"1cfb32e3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:42:40.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the current `fetch_quote()` implementation. It uses `urllib.request` to Tencent directly. I need to update it to use `DataFetcherManager` with THS/TDX priority.\n\nThe key changes:\n1. Add `DataFetcherManager` import from `daily_stock_analysis.data_provider.base`2. Add a new function `fetch_quote_unified()` that uses `DataFetcherManager.get_realtime_quote()`3. The unified fetcher will automatically try THS, Pytdx, then efinance, then others\n4. Keep the old `fetch_quote()` as a fallback\n\nActually, looking at the code more carefully - I should just replace the internal `fetch_quote()` implementation with `DataFetcherManager`, since the unified routing will handle fallback automatically.\n\n\nI'll add the DataFetcherManager import, update `fetch_quote()` to route through it with THS/TDX prioritized, and ensure the fallback to the old Tencent method is in place for compatibility.","thinkingSignature":"716a0efa68245a2b9f310c13434b7c94949568082d99b3c796c463b491243f4e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k4r2c0fkesu2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py","oldText":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport signal\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nANALYZER_TIMEOUT_SEC = 15  # 单只股票分析超时秒数，超时则视为 unavailable\n\nROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = ROOT / 'research' / 'reports'\nDSA_ROOT = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\n\n# ── thresholds for analyzer_service veto ────────────────────────────────────\nSENTIMENT_SCORE_MIN = 40          # below this → block\nNEGATIVE_ADVICES = {\"减仓\", \"卖出\"}\n\n# ── normalise helpers ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nCODE_FIELDS = ['ts_code', 'ticker', 'symbol', 'code', 'stock_code']\nSIDE_FIELDS = ['side', 'action', 'order_side', 'trade_side', 'signal_side']\nBUY_VALUES = {'buy', 'open_buy', 'long', 'b'}\n\n\ndef normalize_symbol(symbol: str) -> str:\n    s = str(symbol or '').strip().upper()\n    if not s:\n        return s\n    s = s.replace('.', '')\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SH', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SZ', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SH\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SZ\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}', s):\n        return ('sh' if s.startswith('6') else 'sz') + s\n    return s.lower()\n\n\n# ── quote ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\ndef fetch_quote(symbol: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    market_symbol = normalize_symbol(symbol)\n    url = f'http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={market_symbol}'\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=8) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode('gbk', errors='ignore')\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'parse_failed'}\n        f = m.group(1).split('~')\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'field_short'}\n        return {\n            'valid': True,\n            'input_symbol': symbol,\n            'market_symbol': market_symbol,\n            'name': f[1] or '',\n            'price': float(f[3] or 0),\n            'change_pct': float(f[32] or 0),\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': repr(e)}","newText":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport signal\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nANALYZER_TIMEOUT_SEC = 15  # 单只股票分析超时秒数，超时则视为 unavailable\n\nROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = ROOT / 'research' / 'reports'\nDSA_ROOT = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\n\n# ── thresholds for analyzer_service veto ────────────────────────────────────\nSENTIMENT_SCORE_MIN = 40          # below this → block\nNEGATIVE_ADVICES = {\"减仓\", \"卖出\"}\n\n# ── normalise helpers ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nCODE_FIELDS = ['ts_code', 'ticker', 'symbol', 'code', 'stock_code']\nSIDE_FIELDS = ['side', 'action', 'order_side', 'trade_side', 'signal_side']\nBUY_VALUES = {'buy', 'open_buy', 'long', 'b'}\n\n\ndef normalize_symbol(symbol: str) -> str:\n    s = str(symbol or '').strip().upper()\n    if not s:\n        return s\n    s = s.replace('.', '')\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SH', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}SZ', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[:6]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SH\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sh' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'SZ\\d{6}', s):\n        return 'sz' + s[2:]\n    if re.fullmatch(r'\\d{6}', s):\n        return ('sh' if s.startswith('6') else 'sz') + s\n    return s.lower()\n\n\ndef _ths_ts_code(symbol: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Convert symbol to THS/TDX format (e.g. 002920.SZ).\"\"\"\n    s = str(symbol or '').strip().upper()\n    s = s.replace('.', '').replace('SH', '').replace('SZ', '')\n    if len(s) == 6:\n        return ('SZ' if s.startswith(('0', '3')) else 'SH') + s\n    # already in format\n    return symbol.upper()\n\n\n# ── unified fetcher (THS/TDX priority) ─────────────────────────────────────\ndef _get_unified_fetcher():\n    \"\"\"Return a configured DataFetcherManager with THS/TDX at highest priority.\"\"\"\n    if str(DSA_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(DSA_ROOT))\n    from data_provider.base import DataFetcherManager\n    from data_provider.efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\n    from data_provider.akshare_fetcher import AkshareFetcher\n    from data_provider.ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher\n    from data_provider.pytdx_fetcher import PytdxFetcher\n    from data_provider.tushare_fetcher import TushareFetcher\n    from data_provider.baostock_fetcher import BaostockFetcher\n\n    fetchers = [\n        ThsMarketFetcher(priority=0),    # 同花顺最高优先级\n        PytdxFetcher(priority=1),       # 通达信次高\n        EfinanceFetcher(priority=2),\n        AkshareFetcher(priority=3),\n        TushareFetcher(priority=4),\n        BaostockFetcher(priority=5),\n    ]\n    return DataFetcherManager(fetchers=fetchers)\n\n\n# ── quote (unified fetcher with THS/TDX priority, fallback to tencent) ──────\ndef fetch_quote(symbol: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    # 方法1：尝试统一路由（THS → Pytdx → Efinance → AkShare）\n    try:\n        manager = _get_unified_fetcher()\n        ts_code = _ths_ts_code(symbol)\n        quote = manager.get_realtime_quote(ts_code)\n        if quote is not None and quote.price is not None and quote.price > 0:\n            return {\n                'valid': True,\n                'input_symbol': symbol,\n                'market_symbol': ts_code,\n                'name': getattr(quote, 'name', '') or '',\n                'price': quote.price,\n                'change_pct': quote.change_pct or 0.0,\n                'source': 'unified_fetcher',\n            }\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n\n    # 方法2：降级到腾讯直连\n    market_symbol = normalize_symbol(symbol)\n    url = f'http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={market_symbol}'\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=8) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode('gbk', errors='ignore')\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'parse_failed'}\n        f = m.group(1).split('~')\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': 'field_short'}\n        return {\n            'valid': True,\n            'input_symbol': symbol,\n            'market_symbol': market_symbol,\n            'name': f[1] or '',\n            'price': float(f[3] or 0),\n            'change_pct': float(f[32] or 0),\n            'source': 'tencent_fallback',\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {'valid': False, 'symbol': symbol, 'reason': repr(e)}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109431,"output":2176,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135900,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931322702}}
