{"type":"message","id":"fac9e3b3","parentId":"3252d1f4","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:15.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the full `intraday_market_gate.py` to understand what I need to modify.","thinkingSignature":"7ce6bae160fbd30c4fe2cf2e1d1d0294d049d3a38985ea0f32ba52941ea87ee3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hmf8pltkt1el_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/intraday_market_gate.py 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109288,"output":76,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931391520}}
{"type":"message","id":"d29969df","parentId":"fac9e3b3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:15.557Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hmf8pltkt1el_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n盘中实时大盘门禁 - 用于在买入推荐生成前检查当日实时大盘状态\n避免用昨日/前一日收盘口径支撑当日买入决策\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport re\nimport ssl\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Optional\n\n# 主要监控的指数代码（腾讯格式）\nINDEX_CODES = {\n    \"sh000001\": \"上证指数\",\n    \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\", \n    \"sz399006\": \"创业板指\",\n    \"sh000852\": \"中证1000\",\n}\n\nINDEX_CODE_LIST = list(INDEX_CODES.keys())\n\n\ndef fetch_tencent_quote(symbol: str, timeout: float = 8.0) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情\"\"\"\n    url = f\"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={symbol}\"\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\")\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return None\n        f = m.group(1).split(\"~\")\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return None\n        price = float(f[3] or 0)\n        change_pct = float(f[32] or 0)\n        return {\n            \"symbol\": symbol,\n            \"name\": f[1] or \"\",\n            \"price\": price,\n            \"change_pct\": change_pct,\n            \"valid\": price > 0,\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef fetch_multi_quote(symbols: list[str]) -> dict[str, dict]:\n    \"\"\"批量获取实时行情\"\"\"\n    results = {}\n    for sym in symbols:\n        quote = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n        if quote:\n            results[sym] = quote\n    return results\n\n\ndef is_trading_hours() -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断当前是否在交易时段（A股）\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    hour = now.hour\n    minute = now.minute\n    # 上午: 09:30-11:30, 下午: 13:00-15:00\n    if hour == 9 and minute < 30:\n        return False\n    if hour == 11 and minute > 30:\n        return False\n    if hour == 12:\n        return False\n    return (hour == 9 and minute >= 30) or (10 <= hour < 11) or (hour == 11 and minute <= 30) or (hour == 13) or (hour == 14) or (hour == 15 and minute == 0)\n\n\ndef evaluate_intraday_market_gate(quotes: dict[str, dict]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    基于实时指数涨跌幅评估盘中市场门禁状态\n    \n    返回:\n    {\n        \"enabled\": bool,  # 是否启用（交易时段且有数据）\n        \"indices\": dict,  # 各指数实时数据\n        \"negative_count\": int,  # 下跌指数数量\n        \"total_count\": int,  # 有效指数总数\n        \"weakness_score\": float,  # 弱势分数 (下跌数/总数)\n        \"gate_action\": str,  # \"none\" | \"cautious\" | \"halt\"\n        \"reason\": str,\n    }\n    \"\"\"\n    if not quotes:\n        return {\n            \"enabled\": False,\n            \"reason\": \"无可用实时指数数据\",\n            \"indices\": {},\n            \"negative_count\": 0,\n            \"total_count\": 0,\n            \"weakness_score\": 0.0,\n            \"gate_action\": \"none\",\n        }\n    \n    valid_quotes = {k: v for k, v in quotes.items() if v.get(\"valid\", False)}\n    if not valid_quotes:\n        return {\n            \"enabled\": False,\n            \"reason\": \"所有指数数据无效\",\n            \"indices\": quotes,\n            \"negative_count\": 0,\n            \"total_count\": 0,\n            \"weakness_score\": 0.0,\n            \"gate_action\": \"none\",\n        }\n    \n    negative_count = sum(1 for v in valid_quotes.values() if v.get(\"change_pct\", 0) < 0)\n    total_count = len(valid_quotes)\n    weakness_score = negative_count / total_count if total_count > 0 else 0.0\n    \n    # 规则：>=3/4 指数下跌 → halt; 2/4 下跌 → cautious\n    if negative_count >= 3:\n        gate_action = \"halt\"\n        reason = f\"{negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，盘中的门禁触发 halt\"\n    elif negative_count >= 2:\n        gate_action = \"cautious\"\n        reason = f\"{negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，盘中进入谨慎模式\"\n    else:\n        gate_action = \"none\"\n        reason = f\"仅 {negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，暂不触发门禁\"\n    \n    return {\n        \"enabled\": True,\n        \"indices\": valid_quotes,\n        \"negative_count\": negative_count,\n        \"total_count\": total_count,\n        \"weakness_score\": weakness_score,\n        \"gate_action\": gate_action,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n    }\n\n\ndef get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    获取指定日期的盘中市场状态\n    \n    如果日期是今天且在交易时段，返回实时指数门禁评估结果\n    否则返回 {\"enabled\": False}\n    \"\"\"\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    \n    # 只有今天是交易日且在交易时段才获取实时数据\n    if date_tag != today:\n        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n    \n    if not is_trading_hours():\n        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}\n    \n    quotes = fetch_multi_quote(INDEX_CODE_LIST)\n    gate_result = evaluate_intraday_market_gate(quotes)\n    \n    return gate_result\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import sys\n    date_arg = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    result = get_intraday_market_state(date_arg)\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n盘中实时大盘门禁 - 用于在买入推荐生成前检查当日实时大盘状态\n避免用昨日/前一日收盘口径支撑当日买入决策\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport re\nimport ssl\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Optional\n\n# 主要监控的指数代码（腾讯格式）\nINDEX_CODES = {\n    \"sh000001\": \"上证指数\",\n    \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\", \n    \"sz399006\": \"创业板指\",\n    \"sh000852\": \"中证1000\",\n}\n\nINDEX_CODE_LIST = list(INDEX_CODES.keys())\n\n\ndef fetch_tencent_quote(symbol: str, timeout: float = 8.0) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情\"\"\"\n    url = f\"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={symbol}\"\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\")\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return None\n        f = m.group(1).split(\"~\")\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return None\n        price = float(f[3] or 0)\n        change_pct = float(f[32] or 0)\n        return {\n            \"symbol\": symbol,\n            \"name\": f[1] or \"\",\n            \"price\": price,\n            \"change_pct\": change_pct,\n            \"valid\": price > 0,\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef fetch_multi_quote(symbols: list[str]) -> dict[str, dict]:\n    \"\"\"批量获取实时行情\"\"\"\n    results = {}\n    for sym in symbols:\n        quote = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n        if quote:\n            results[sym] = quote\n    return results\n\n\ndef is_trading_hours() -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断当前是否在交易时段（A股）\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    hour = now.hour\n    minute = now.minute\n    # 上午: 09:30-11:30, 下午: 13:00-15:00\n    if hour == 9 and minute < 30:\n        return False\n    if hour == 11 and minute > 30:\n        return False\n    if hour == 12:\n        return False\n    return (hour == 9 and minute >= 30) or (10 <= hour < 11) or (hour == 11 and minute <= 30) or (hour == 13) or (hour == 14) or (hour == 15 and minute == 0)\n\n\ndef evaluate_intraday_market_gate(quotes: dict[str, dict]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    基于实时指数涨跌幅评估盘中市场门禁状态\n    \n    返回:\n    {\n        \"enabled\": bool,  # 是否启用（交易时段且有数据）\n        \"indices\": dict,  # 各指数实时数据\n        \"negative_count\": int,  # 下跌指数数量\n        \"total_count\": int,  # 有效指数总数\n        \"weakness_score\": float,  # 弱势分数 (下跌数/总数)\n        \"gate_action\": str,  # \"none\" | \"cautious\" | \"halt\"\n        \"reason\": str,\n    }\n    \"\"\"\n    if not quotes:\n        return {\n            \"enabled\": False,\n            \"reason\": \"无可用实时指数数据\",\n            \"indices\": {},\n            \"negative_count\": 0,\n            \"total_count\": 0,\n            \"weakness_score\": 0.0,\n            \"gate_action\": \"none\",\n        }\n    \n    valid_quotes = {k: v for k, v in quotes.items() if v.get(\"valid\", False)}\n    if not valid_quotes:\n        return {\n            \"enabled\": False,\n            \"reason\": \"所有指数数据无效\",\n            \"indices\": quotes,\n            \"negative_count\": 0,\n            \"total_count\": 0,\n            \"weakness_score\": 0.0,\n            \"gate_action\": \"none\",\n        }\n    \n    negative_count = sum(1 for v in valid_quotes.values() if v.get(\"change_pct\", 0) < 0)\n    total_count = len(valid_quotes)\n    weakness_score = negative_count / total_count if total_count > 0 else 0.0\n    \n    # 规则：>=3/4 指数下跌 → halt; 2/4 下跌 → cautious\n    if negative_count >= 3:\n        gate_action = \"halt\"\n        reason = f\"{negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，盘中的门禁触发 halt\"\n    elif negative_count >= 2:\n        gate_action = \"cautious\"\n        reason = f\"{negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，盘中进入谨慎模式\"\n    else:\n        gate_action = \"none\"\n        reason = f\"仅 {negative_count}/{total_count} 指数下跌，暂不触发门禁\"\n    \n    return {\n        \"enabled\": True,\n        \"indices\": valid_quotes,\n        \"negative_count\": negative_count,\n        \"total_count\": total_count,\n        \"weakness_score\": weakness_score,\n        \"gate_action\": gate_action,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n    }\n\n\ndef get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    获取指定日期的盘中市场状态\n    \n    如果日期是今天且在交易时段，返回实时指数门禁评估结果\n    否则返回 {\"enabled\": False}\n    \"\"\"\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    \n    # 只有今天是交易日且在交易时段才获取实时数据\n    if date_tag != today:\n        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n    \n    if not is_trading_hours():\n        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}\n    \n    quotes = fetch_multi_quote(INDEX_CODE_LIST)\n    gate_result = evaluate_intraday_market_gate(quotes)\n    \n    return gate_result\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import sys\n    date_arg = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    result = get_intraday_market_state(date_arg)\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931395544}}
{"type":"message","id":"df334ea2","parentId":"d29969df","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:31.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `intraday_market_gate.py` focuses on index data (sh000001, sz399001, sz399006, sh000852). The THS/TDX unified fetcher can handle indices too. But the main issue is that the script is not using the unified fetcher.\n\nHowever, updating `intraday_market_gate.py` to use the unified fetcher is more complex because it uses index codes in Tencent format (`sh000001`, `sz399001`, etc.) rather than stock codes. The unified fetcher may not support these index codes in the same format.\n\nLet me focus on what's practical:\n1. ✅ Already updated `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` - done\n\n\n2. For `intraday_market_gate.py` - the indices can be fetched through efinance or yfinance via the unified fetcher, but the Tencent format works fine as a fallback. Since the core entry point (`stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`) now prioritizes THS/TDX, I'll document the current state and next steps rather than over-engineering this script.","thinkingSignature":"284fed69e48947b9f61046de4194b1fab5a5a35cef154d2937e7034a23fc0eb3"},{"type":"text","text":"核心入口 `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` 已更新完毕。现在 commit：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_or6ej78mikth_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && git add quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py && git commit -m \"feat: stock_level_realtime_gate_v2 use DataFetcherManager with THS/TDX priority\n\n- fetch_quote() now tries unified DataFetcherManager first (THS → Pytdx → Efinance → AkShare)\n- Falls back to Tencent urllib on failure\n- Adds 'source' field to quote result for traceability\n- Result for 002920: THS/TDX timeout → Tencent fallback successful\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108647,"output":390,"cacheRead":24293,"cache