{"type":"message","id":"9eba3c61","parentId":"774b04e8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:47.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the `intraday_market_gate.py`. For index data, the unified fetcher can handle index quotes via efinance or yfinance. Let me update the fetcher to use the unified approach.\n\nActually, the indices use Tencent format (`sh000001`). The unified fetcher's `get_realtime_quote` might not handle these index codes well. Let me check if the THS/TDX can handle these codes.\n\nActually, the simplest and most impactful change is already done - `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` now uses the unified fetcher with THS/TDX priority. \n\nLet me also update `intraday_market_gate.py` to use the unified fetcher, since it's a critical entry point too. The indices can be fetched via `EfinanceFetcher` or `YfinanceFetcher` from the unified manager.","thinkingSignature":"80b2b6116b3170e9072236f1ae9cbbcbf34bf6ebf016f58206a8cadef151fb2f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g2fepo6oupnz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis && python3 -c \"\nimport sys; sys.path.insert(0,'.')\nfrom data_provider.base import DataFetcherManager\nfrom data_provider.efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\nfrom data_provider.yfinance_fetcher import YfinanceFetcher\nfrom data_provider.ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher\nfrom data_provider.pytdx_fetcher import PytdxFetcher\n\nfetchers = [ThsMarketFetcher(priority=0), PytdxFetcher(priority=1), EfinanceFetcher(priority=2), YfinanceFetcher(priority=4)]\nmgr = DataFetcherManager(fetchers=fetchers)\n# 试指数\nfor code in ['000001.SH', '399001.SZ', '399006.SZ', '000852.SH']:\n    q = mgr.get_realtime_quote(code)\n    print(f'{code}: {q.price if q else None}, {q.change_pct if q else None}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108701