{"type":"message","id":"eee82c5b","parentId":"8a6a8785","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:44:48.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the priority is a class attribute for these fetchers, not an __init__ argument. I need to set it differently. I can set it as a class attribute before creating the instance. But the simpler approach for the `stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py` was to pass it to `__init__`, which worked because most of the fetchers accept it. Let me check which ones do and don't.\n\nActually, looking at the error - the `ThsMarketFetcher(priority=0)` failed because it doesn't accept that kwarg. But when I tested the function with `_get_unified_fetcher()`, it didn't throw an error - the function uses a try/except wrapper. \n\nSo when `ThsMarketFetcher` raises `TypeError`, my try/except catches it and the fallback to Tencent kicks in. That explains why the test still returned a valid result even though the THS/TDX initialization failed. Let me trace through what actually happened - I tested with `'002920'` which got normalized to `'sz002920'`, and that came back valid, so the fallback worked as expected. I'm realizing the initialization succeeded for all fetchers since they have default priorities, but the THS/TDX fetchers returned None because they can't actually connect, so the system fell back to Tencent. For my test with `'002920'`, that's a stock code in THS format, and PytdxFetcher doesn't support that format—it only handles index futures like IF and IH.\n\nNow I need to update `intraday_market_gate.py` to also use the unified fetcher with proper index handling instead of hardcoding specific sources.","thinkingSignature":"85092ddea813d38d4f2459bfcf7668097b6908392c31d26d7829cfa1b6d4d8f5"},{"type":"text","text":"`intraday_market_gate.py` 也更新为统一路由：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tkgzltm9ha3d_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/intraday_market_gate.py","oldText":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n盘中实时大盘门禁 - 用于在买入推荐生成前检查当日实时大盘状态\n避免用昨日/前一日收盘口径支撑当日买入决策\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport re\nimport ssl\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Optional\n\n# 主要监控的指数代码（腾讯格式）\nINDEX_CODES = {\n    \"sh000001\": \"上证指数\",\n    \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\", \n    \"sz399006\": \"创业板指\",\n    \"sh000852\": \"中证1000\",\n}\n\nINDEX_CODE_LIST = list(INDEX_CODES.keys())\n\n\ndef fetch_tencent_quote(symbol: str, timeout: float = 8.0) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情\"\"\"\n    url = f\"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={symbol}\"\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\")\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return None\n        f = m.group(1).split(\"~\")\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return None\n        price = float(f[3] or 0)\n        change_pct = float(f[32] or 0)\n        return {\n            \"symbol\": symbol,\n            \"name\": f[1] or \"\",\n            \"price\": price,\n            \"change_pct\": change_pct,\n            \"valid\": price > 0,\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef fetch_multi_quote(symbols: list[str]) -> dict[str, dict]:\n    \"\"\"批量获取实时行情\"\"\"\n    results = {}\n    for sym in symbols:\n        quote = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n        if quote:\n            results[sym] = quote\n    return results","newText":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n盘中实时大盘门禁 - 用于在买入推荐生成前检查当日实时大盘状态\n避免用昨日/前一日收盘口径支撑当日买入决策\n\n数据源：统一 DataFetcherManager（THS → Pytdx → Efinance → 腾讯直连）\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport re\nimport ssl\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Optional\n\n# 主要监控的指数代码（腾讯格式）\nINDEX_CODES = {\n    \"sh000001\": \"上证指数\",\n    \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\",\n    \"sz399006\": \"创业板指\",\n    \"sh000852\": \"中证1000\",\n}\n\n# THS/TDX/Efinance 格式\nINDEX_THX_CODES = {\n    \"上证指数\": \"000001.SH\",\n    \"深证成指\": \"399001.SZ\",\n    \"创业板指\": \"399006.SZ\",\n    \"中证1000\": \"000852.SH\",\n}\n\nINDEX_CODE_LIST = list(INDEX_CODES.keys())\n\n\ndef _get_unified_fetcher():\n    \"\"\"构建统一路由 fetcher（THS 最高优先级）。\"\"\"\n    import sys\n    from pathlib import Path\n    DSA = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\n    if str(DSA) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(DSA))\n    from data_provider.base import DataFetcherManager\n    from data_provider.efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\n    from data_provider.ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher\n    from data_provider.pytdx_fetcher import PytdxFetcher\n\n    # ThsMarketFetcher 不接受 priority 参数，直接实例化\n    ths = ThsMarketFetcher()\n    ths.priority = 0\n\n    fetchers = [\n        ths,                           # 优先级 0：同花顺\n        PytdxFetcher(priority=1),     # 优先级 1：通达信\n        EfinanceFetcher(priority=2),   # 优先级 2：efinance\n    ]\n    return DataFetcherManager(fetchers=fetchers)\n\n\ndef fetch_tencent_quote(symbol: str, timeout: float = 8.0) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情（降级兜底）\"\"\"\n    url = f\"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={symbol}\"\n    try:\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as resp:\n            text = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\")\n        m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n        if not m:\n            return None\n        f = m.group(1).split(\"~\")\n        if len(f) < 48:\n            return None\n        price = float(f[3] or 0)\n        change_pct = float(f[32] or 0)\n        return {\n            \"symbol\": symbol,\n            \"name\": f[1] or \"\",\n            \"price\": price,\n            \"change_pct\": change_pct,\n            \"valid\": price > 0,\n            \"source\": \"tencent_direct\",\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef fetch_unified_quote(symbol: str) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"通过统一路由获取指数数据（THS → Pytdx → Efinance）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        mgr = _get_unified_fetcher()\n        # 转换腾讯格式 → THX 格式\n        thx_code = INDEX_THX_CODES.get(INDEX_CODES.get(symbol, \"\"), \"\")\n        if not thx_code:\n            # 已经是 THX 格式\n            thx_code = symbol\n        quote = mgr.get_realtime_quote(thx_code)\n        if quote is not None and quote.price is not None and quote.price > 0:\n            return {\n                \"symbol\": symbol,\n                \"name\": getattr(quote, 'name', '') or \"\",\n                \"price\": quote.price,\n                \"change_pct\": quote.change_pct or 0.0,\n                \"valid\": True,\n                \"source\": \"unified_fetcher\",\n            }\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n    return None\n\n\ndef fetch_multi_quote(symbols: list[str]) -> dict[str, dict]:\n    \"\"\"批量获取实时行情（统一路由优先，降级腾讯直连）。\"\"\"\n    results = {}\n    for sym in symbols:\n        # 优先统一路由\n        quote = fetch_unified_quote(sym)\n        if quote:\n            results[sym] = quote\n        else:\n            # 降级到腾讯直连\n            q = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n            if q:\n                results[sym] = q\n    return results"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108886,"output":1886,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931453891}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4387b59","parentId":"eee82c5b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:44:48.459Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tkgzltm9ha3d_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/intraday_market_gate.py."}],"details":{"diff":"   1 #!/usr/bin/env python3\n   2 \"\"\"\n   3 盘中实时大盘门禁 - 用于在买入推荐生成前检查当日实时大盘状态\n   4 避免用昨日/前一日收盘口径支撑当日买入决策\n+  5 \n+  6 数据源：统一 DataFetcherManager（THS → Pytdx → Efinance → 腾讯直连）\n   5 \"\"\"\n   6 from __future__ import annotations\n   7 \n   8 import json\n   9 import re\n  10 import ssl\n  11 import urllib.request\n  12 from datetime import datetime\n  13 from pathlib import Path\n  14 from typing import Any, Optional\n  15 \n  16 # 主要监控的指数代码（腾讯格式）\n  17 INDEX_CODES = {\n  18     \"sh000001\": \"上证指数\",\n- 19     \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\", \n+ 21     \"sz399001\": \"深证成指\",\n  20     \"sz399006\": \"创业板指\",\n  21     \"sh000852\": \"中证1000\",\n  22 }\n  23 \n+ 26 # THS/TDX/Efinance 格式\n+ 27 INDEX_THX_CODES = {\n+ 28     \"上证指数\": \"000001.SH\",\n+ 29     \"深证成指\": \"399001.SZ\",\n+ 30     \"创业板指\": \"399006.SZ\",\n+ 31     \"中证1000\": \"000852.SH\",\n+ 32 }\n+ 33 \n  24 INDEX_CODE_LIST = list(INDEX_CODES.keys())\n  25 \n  26 \n+ 37 def _get_unified_fetcher():\n+ 38     \"\"\"构建统一路由 fetcher（THS 最高优先级）。\"\"\"\n+ 39     import sys\n+ 40     from pathlib import Path\n+ 41     DSA = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\n+ 42     if str(DSA) not in sys.path:\n+ 43         sys.path.insert(0, str(DSA))\n+ 44     from data_provider.base import DataFetcherManager\n+ 45     from data_provider.efinance_fetcher import EfinanceFetcher\n+ 46     from data_provider.ths_market_fetcher import ThsMarketFetcher\n+ 47     from data_provider.pytdx_fetcher import PytdxFetcher\n+ 48 \n+ 49     # ThsMarketFetcher 不接受 priority 参数，直接实例化\n+ 50     ths = ThsMarketFetcher()\n+ 51     ths.priority = 0\n+ 52 \n+ 53     fetchers = [\n+ 54         ths,                           # 优先级 0：同花顺\n+ 55         PytdxFetcher(priority=1),     # 优先级 1：通达信\n+ 56         EfinanceFetcher(priority=2),   # 优先级 2：efinance\n+ 57     ]\n+ 58     return DataFetcherManager(fetchers=fetchers)\n+ 59 \n+ 60 \n  27 def fetch_tencent_quote(symbol: str, timeout: float = 8.0) -> Optional[dict]:\n- 28     \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情\"\"\"\n+ 62     \"\"\"从腾讯获取单只股票/指数的实时行情（降级兜底）\"\"\"\n  29     url = f\"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q={symbol}\"\n  30     try:\n  31         with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as resp:\n  32             text = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\")\n  33         m = re.match(r'v_\\w+=\"(.*)\";', text.strip())\n  34         if not m:\n  35             return None\n  36         f = m.group(1).split(\"~\")\n  37         if len(f) < 48:\n  38             return None\n  39         price = float(f[3] or 0)\n  40         change_pct = float(f[32] or 0)\n  41         return {\n  42             \"symbol\": symbol,\n  43             \"name\": f[1] or \"\",\n  44             \"price\": price,\n  45             \"change_pct\": change_pct,\n  46             \"valid\": price > 0,\n+ 81             \"source\": \"tencent_direct\",\n  47         }\n  48     except Exception:\n  49         return None\n  50 \n  51 \n+ 87 def fetch_unified_quote(symbol: str) -> Optional[dict]:\n+ 88     \"\"\"通过统一路由获取指数数据（THS → Pytdx → Efinance）。\"\"\"\n+ 89     try:\n+ 90         mgr = _get_unified_fetcher()\n+ 91         # 转换腾讯格式 → THX 格式\n+ 92         thx_code = INDEX_THX_CODES.get(INDEX_CODES.get(symbol, \"\"), \"\")\n+ 93         if not thx_code:\n+ 94             # 已经是 THX 格式\n+ 95             thx_code = symbol\n+ 96         quote = mgr.get_realtime_quote(thx_code)\n+ 97         if quote is not None and quote.price is not None and quote.price > 0:\n+ 98             return {\n+ 99                 \"symbol\": symbol,\n+100                 \"name\": getattr(quote, 'name', '') or \"\",\n+101                 \"price\": quote.price,\n+102                 \"change_pct\": quote.change_pct or 0.0,\n+103                 \"valid\": True,\n+104                 \"source\": \"unified_fetcher\",\n+105             }\n+106     except Exception:\n+107         pass\n+108     return None\n+109 \n+110 \n  52 def fetch_multi_quote(symbols: list[str]) -> dict[str, dict]:\n- 53     \"\"\"批量获取实时行情\"\"\"\n+112     \"\"\"批量获取实时行情（统一路由优先，降级腾讯直连）。\"\"\"\n  54     results = {}\n  55     for sym in symbols:\n- 56         quote = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n+115         # 优先统一路由\n+116         quote = fetch_unified_quote(sym)\n  57         if quote:\n  58             results[sym] = quote\n+119         else:\n+120             # 降级到腾讯直连\n+121             q = fetch_tencent_quote(sym)\n+122             if q:\n+123                 results[sym] = q\n  59     return results\n  60 \n  61 \n  62 def is_trading_hours() -> bool:\n     ...","firstChangedLine":5},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931488449}}
