n- 若 Windows 环境有 THS 终端：THS 会以最高优先级工作\n- 若 Pytdx 网络恢复：Pytdx 以次优先级工作\n- `intraday_market_breadth.py` 需要单独补充 breadth 路由方法（暂无统一接口）","oldText":"## 融合现状总结\n\n| 层次 | 状态 | 证据 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 第一层 | ✅ 已落地 | stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py |\n| 第二层 | ✅ 已落地 | run_premarket_risk_v2.py |\n| 第三层 | ✅ 已落地 | run_close_review_v2.py |\n| 报告 | ✅ 已出 | stock_analyzer_gate_integration_progress_20260319.md |","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/stock_analyzer_gate_integration_progress_20260319.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107635,"output":747,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931530367}}
