{"type":"message","id":"c7d8a160","parentId":"44ebdd82","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:56:17.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. When `FORCE_REFRESH=1`, the script does call `ensure_same_day_live_system` (which runs `run_live_system_v1.py`), but `ensure_same_day_merged_signals` (which runs `prepare_live_signal_tickets.py`) is only called when the merged file doesn't exist - it doesn't get the `--force-rebuild` flag.\n\nAlso, the message `force rebuilding same-day live system` isn't present - the `ensure_same_day_live_system` function just says \"materializing same-day live system\".\n\nThe fix is:\n1. When `FORCE_REFRESH=1`, the `ensure_same_day_merged_signals` should also be called with `--force-rebuild`\n\n\n2. Add `force rebuilding same-day live system` log message to `ensure_same_day_live_system`\n\nNow I need to examine the full `run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh` file to understand how to properly implement these changes.","thinkingSignature":"e8dca3596330d4fcd1c366ad43f3b1c3f71a37e1bb3e3438affcfe011df76f62"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l5b1pe5i3c5v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '60,125p' ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112979,"output":265,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137537,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773932166841}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ca491dc","parentId":"c7d8a160","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:56:17.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l5b1pe5i3c5v_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"print(payload.get(\"available_cash\", 1000000))\nprint(payload.get(\"account_nav\", payload.get(\"available_cash\", 1000000)))\nPY\n}\n\nensure_same_day_merged_signals() {\n  local sizing available_cash account_nav\n  sizing=\"$(read_live_sizing)\"\n  available_cash=\"$(printf '%s\\n' \"$sizing\" | sed -n '1p')\"\n  account_nav=\"$(printf '%s\\n' \"$sizing\" | sed -n '2p')\"\n  echo \"[INFO] missing merged_signals, materializing same-day live signal chain date=${DATE_TAG}\"\n  python3 scripts/prepare_live_signal_tickets.py \\\n    --date \"$DATE_TAG\" \\\n    --available-cash \"$available_cash\" \\\n    --account-nav \"$account_nav\"\n}\n\nensure_same_day_live_system() {\n  if [[ \"$DATE_TAG\" != \"$TODAY_TAG\" ]]; then\n    return 0\n  fi\n  echo \"[INFO] missing live_system, materializing same-day live system date=${DATE_TAG}\"\n  python3 scripts/run_live_system_v1.py\n}\n\nMERGED_FILE=\"$ROOT/signals/merged/merged_signals_${DATE_TAG}.csv\"\ncheck_runtime_halt_before_profiles || exit $?\n\nif [[ \"${FORCE_REFRESH:-0}\" == \"1\" || ! -f \"$LIVE_SYSTEM_FILE\" ]]; then\n  ensure_same_day_live_system\nfi\n\nif [[ ! -f \"$LIVE_SYSTEM_FILE\" ]]; then\n  echo \"[ERROR] 缺少当日 live_system: $LIVE_SYSTEM_FILE\"\n  exit 2\nfi\n\nif [[ -z \"$TICKETS_FILE\" && ! -f \"$MERGED_FILE\" ]]; then\n  ensure_same_day_merged_signals\nfi\n\nif [[ -z \"$TICKETS_FILE\" && ! -f \"$MERGED_FILE\" ]]; then\n  echo \"[ERROR] 缺少当日 merged_signals: $MERGED_FILE\"\n  exit 2\nfi\n\nrun_once() {\n  if [[ -n \"$TICKETS_FILE\" ]]; then\n    bash scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh \"$DATE_TAG\" \"$TICKETS_FILE\"\n  else\n    bash scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh \"$DATE_TAG\"\n  fi\n}\n\nattempt=1\nwhile (( attempt <= RETRY_MAX )); do\n  echo \"[RUN] paper_profiles attempt