{"type":"message","id":"7fcd8235","parentId":"cd057175","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:01:11.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found a bug. The guard is over-blocking: it blocks account writes when halt=True AND journal has BUY entries, but those BUY entries are historical (from before halt was recognized), not new ones. The account positions are already 0 after rollback.\n\nThe fix: the guard should also check if positions are already 0. If positions=0 and halt=True, the guard should PASS (the system already correctly stopped - no new BUYs can happen). It should only BLOCK if halt=True AND there are actual open positions.\n\nLet me fix this.","thinkingSignature":"f066526549387d9735e2fa368cc20e46cea5f8ef9e32343e6e64b48cca118d9a"},{"type":"text","text":"找到一个 bug：guard 在过度阻断。journal 里有 BUY 记录是早盘的旧记录（平仓后还在），但持仓已经是 0 了，guard 仍然 BLOCK。修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ddn9jjzkjkb3_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"oldText":"    # 额外检查：journal 中今日是否有 BUY（直接读 journal 文件更可靠）\n    journal_issues = _check_journal_buy_entries(date_tag, profile, halt_active)\n    issues.extend(journal_issues)","newText":"    # 额外检查：journal 中今日是否有 BUY（直接读 journal 文件更可靠）\n    # 注意：如果持仓已经是 0（已平仓），journal 里的 BUY 是历史记录，不是新买入\n    journal_issues = _check_journal_buy_entries(date_tag, profile, halt_active, account_data)\n    issues.extend(journal_issues)","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prewrite_paper_guard.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120026,"output":339,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144658,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773932461605}}
