{"type":"message","id":"8785bb17","parentId":"fefeb4aa","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:13:15.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HEARTBEAT.md doesn't mention ACTIVE_TASK. Let me add a section to it that checks for active tasks.Actually, let me think about this more carefully. The heartbeat runs in the main session. If the main session is busy executing a multi-step task, the heartbeat will fire and potentially interfere. If the main session is idle, the heartbeat can notice that there's an ACTIVE_TASK.md with active status and send a message to continue.\n\nBut actually, the heartbeat already runs as a separate isolated session (`session=isolated` based on the cron setup). The issue is that the main session's heartbeat is triggered by the system polling, not by the cron.\n\nLet me look at the HEARTBEAT.md more carefully:","thinkingSignature":"a5ae2a8f6951fd02d0d4d1348492d0942fe09dd690314af9ded947170a25e81f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gt56rbr7hfez_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120260,"output":186,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144739,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773933187117}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0414bad","parentId":"8785bb17","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:13:15.041Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gt56rbr7hfez_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773933195035}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5fab8b8","parentId":"a0414bad","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:13:33.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the HEARTBEAT.md doesn't mention checking ACTIVE_TASK.md. Let me add a section for active task monitoring.\n\nBut there's a critical issue: the HEARTBEAT.md says it runs as a polling mechanism in the main session. When the heartbeat fires, it fires in the main session, which would interrupt any ongoing task. This could be disruptive.\n\nHowever, the heartbeat is primarily for monitoring and alerting, not for continuing tasks. The cron job I just created (`主动任务续跑检查`) is the right mechanism for automated continuation.\n\nLet me add an entry to HEARTBEAT.md for active task monitoring, but keep it lightweight (just check and log, don't actively continue in the main session).","thinkingSignature":"289801b9458d0257a0b7bc27377fa593bb2ffd3f2a4f1736ff219c22af496799"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_doo5eik8o8ld_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md << 'EOF'\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\nEOF\necho \"added\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120221,"output":323,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144837,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773933195044}}
