{"type":"message","id":"d7df0215","parentId":"630228f6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:13:51.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also think about the practical fix. The issue the user describes is specifically: when I was in the middle of the multi-step task (the three layers, the THS/TDX fixes, the self-checks), after completing one step, I'd send the report and the system would stop until the user triggered the next one.\n\nThe key fix I should apply right now:\n1. When ACTIVE_TASK.md is active and has a Next item, after completing Current, I should spawn a sub-agent to continue the next item, OR use `sessions_yield` to allow the system to continue.\n\nBut `sessions_yield` hands control back to the orchestrator/parent. \n\nSince there's no parent here, it might just end the turn. Using `sessions_spawn` with mode=\"session\" would create a persistent sub-agent that continues independently, which is probably the better approach for keeping the task chain running without waiting for user input.","thinkingSignature":"7ea09023a730d7786fa3f762eff5bfbad07e690d8d03c0e8f4292def7223553c"},{"type":"text","text":"还有一个问题需要解决：ACTIVE_TASK.md 更新后 session turn 就结束了，需要在回复里主动触发下一项。最可靠的方案是用 `sessions_spawn` 创建后台续跑子会话：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ldesoipdx38g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\n# 检查 ACTIVE_TASK.md 当前状态\nwith open('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md') as f:\n    content = f.read()\nprint(content[:500])\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120479,"output":303,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773933213713}}
{"type":"message","id":"f5b74ec5","parentId":"d7df0215","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:13:51.397Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ldesoipdx38g_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-19\nUpdated: 2026-03-19 22:51\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\n\n## Goal\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## Acceptance\n- ✅ 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链（stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py）\n- ✅ 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版（apply_paper_rollback.py）\n- ✅ 下午自动重跑强制刷新链具备机器可检验能力（run_intraday_risk_recheck.py）\n- ✅ 多源实时宽度兜底（intraday_market_breadth.py，三源：AkShare→eFinance→Tushare）\n- ✅ 写账户前 Python 深层阻断（prewrite_paper_guard.py v2）\n- ✅ THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链（DataFetcherManager +"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"Status: done\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-19\nUpdated: 2026-03-19 22:51\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\n\n## Goal\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## Acceptance\n- ✅ 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链（stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py）\n- ✅ 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版（apply_paper_rollback.py）\n- ✅ 下午自动重跑强制刷新链具备机器可检验能力（run_intraday_risk_recheck.py）\n- ✅ 多源实时宽度兜底（intraday_market_breadth.py，三源：AkShare→eFinance→Tushare）\n- ✅ 写账户前 Python 深层阻断（prewrite_paper_guard.py v2）\n- ✅ THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链（DataFetcherManager +","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773933231386}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fd12adf","parentId":"f5b74ec5","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:14:06.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ACTIVE_TASK.md is done. Now let me summarize the findings and the solution to the user.\n\nThe key things I've done:\n1. Created `run_active_task_continuer.py` - a script that checks ACTIVE_TASK.md and can trigger continuation\n2. Created a cron job \"主动任务续跑检查\" that runs every 30 minutes and uses this script\n3. Updated HEARTBEAT.md to include Active Task Monitoring\n\nNow the user asked \"你检查一下openclaw在执行连续多步骤任务时容易完成一个后不执行下一个的问题\". I've identified the issue and set up a solution.","thinkingSignature":"ebf7e812593ec9d2b43c66537ba57fb711f6478489602468ccb77cca26342ef5"},{"type":"text","text":"**检查结果 + 修复方案：**\n\n**问题定位**：\nACTIVE_TASK.md 是\"恢复铁轨\"，不是\"自动引擎\"。系统只能在两种情况下继续：\n1. 用户发新消息触发\n2. Session 重启后恢复\n\n完成步骤→更新文件→回复用户→**turn 结束，系统等待**，这是设计上的断点。\n\n**已部署的修复**：\n\n1. **定时自动续跑任务**（刚创建）\n   - 每 30 分钟检查 `ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n   - 若 Status=active 且有 Next → 自动发信号触发继续\n   - ID: `b2818217`\n\n2. **`HEARTBEAT.md` 增加主动任务监控**（刚更新）\n   - 心跳时检查 ACTIVE_TASK.md\n   - 有 active + pending 项 → 立即续跑\n\n3. **`run_active_task_continuer.py`**（新建）\n   - 专用脚本：检查状态 + cooldowm + 自动续跑\n   - 支持 `--dry-run` 测试\n\n现在即使我不主动触发，下次定时任务（最多等 30 分钟）会自动检查并继续。\n\n当前 ACTIVE_TASK.md 状态是 done（全部完成），所以续跑器会跳过。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119799,"output":384,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144476,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773933231401}}
